NK016(ma)007:0: na rag dong sprugs kyi cho ga bde chen lam bzang zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)007:1: na rag dong sprugs rnal 'byor gyi spyi khrus chen
NK016(ma)007:2: po'i cho ga bde chen lam bzang zhes bya ba
NK016(ma)007:3: / dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:4: rigs brgya'i khyab bdag dpal ldan rdo rje sems //
NK016(ma)007:5: drin chen bla ma mchog dang dbyer med gang //
NK016(ma)007:6: bgrang yas zhi khro rab 'byams dkyil 'khor lhar //
NK016(ma)007:7: mngon par snang mdzad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:8: theg mchog gsang chen lha sngags rnal 'byor gyis //
NK016(ma)007:9: spang bya'i sgrib kun sbyangs nas ye shes lha'i //
NK016(ma)007:10: 'khor lor rgyas 'debs byed pa rnal 'byor spyi'i //
NK016(ma)007:11: cho ga bde chen lam bzang 'dir gsal bya //
NK016(ma)007:12: de la 'dir dpal rdo rje sems dpa' gsang chen
NK016(ma)007:13: rigs gcig gi sgo nas nyams su len pa'i tshul
NK016(ma)007:22: dang po bsang chu sgrub pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:23: bdag nyid skad cig gis rdo rje he ru kar
NK016(ma)007:24: gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h'u las ram yam kham 'phros
NK016(ma)007:25: pas ma dag pa'i dngos 'dzin thams cad bsregs gtor
NK016(ma)007:26: sbyangs / stong pa'i ngang las bsang chu'i steng du /
NK016(ma)007:28: nyi ma la gnas pa'i h'u yig dmar po /
NK016(ma)007:30: sam ha ra na h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:32: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u phata /
NK016(ma)007:33: khro mo dbyings phyug ma dmar mo dril bu dang b+han dmar 'dzin pa'i skur gyur /
NK016(ma)007:34: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgyas reg la /
NK016(ma)007:35: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sarba dra b+y+aam sho d+ha ya +aahmh'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK016(ma)007:36: brgya rtsa brgyad kyis byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK016(ma)007:37: khro mo dbyings phyug ma'i rang bzhin gyi chu'i rdul phra rab tu gyur par bsams /
NK016(ma)007:38: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sarba dra b+y+aam shwa d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)007:39: ces bdag dang gnas yo byad thams cad la bsang gtor bya zhing /
NK016(ma)007:40: thog mtha' kun tu gsang gtor gyi bya ba thams cad 'dis bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:41: gnyis pa gzhi bgegs kyi gtor ma ni /
NK016(ma)007:42: gtor ma dkar dmar rgyan ldan gnyis bshams pa bsang sbyangs /
NK016(ma)007:43: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum las rin po che'i snod
NK016(ma)007:44: zab cing rgya che ba'i nang du gtor ma kha
NK016(ma)007:45: dog dri ro nus pa phun sum tshogs par bsam
NK016(ma)007:48: s+tha na pa ti k+she tra p+aa lany+tsa na mahsarba
NK016(ma)007:49: ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs gsum gyis bsngosa la
NK016(ma)007:50: / gang dag 'dir gnas lha dang klu //
NK016(ma)007:51: gnod sbyon srin po'am gzhan dag la //
NK016(ma)007:53: bdag zhu khyed kyis stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:56: sarba big+h+n+aam namahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs kyis bsngosa la /
NK016(ma)007:59: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //
NK016(ma)007:60: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK016(ma)007:61: thams cad thugs rjes bskangs zin gyis //
NK016(ma)007:62: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK016(ma)007:64: rdo rje khro bo'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK016(ma)007:65: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK016(ma)007:66: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)007:67: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha sogs brjod cing /
NK016(ma)007:70: rol mo'i tsham rngams dang bcas pas bskrad de gtor ma phyir dor /
NK016(ma)007:71: gsum pa rten gyi dkyil 'khor 'du bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:72: dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi la ba byung gis byug /
NK016(ma)007:73: dri bzang dang bdud rtsi lngas chag chag btab la /
NK016(ma)007:74: thig skud dri zhim pa'i thig chal gyis spags pa 'du byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:75: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po yab yum du
NK016(ma)007:76: gsal ba snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK016(ma)007:77: thig skud dang ro gcig pa ye shes lnga'i ngo
NK016(ma)007:81: dang por shar nub gyi tshangs thig gdab pa nas
NK016(ma)007:82: bzung thig chen brgyad po dkyil 'khor gyi mkha' la
NK016(ma)007:83: gdab cing / de bzhin du sa la yang gdab ste /
NK016(ma)007:85: dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+au tra ma ti kra ma h'u /
NK016(ma)007:87: tshul des gzhal yas khang phyi'i khog rta babs brgyad pa sgyu 'phrul zhi ba ltar las /
NK016(ma)007:88: 'og gzhi 'khor lo'i don du sna tshogs rdo rje dang /
NK016(ma)007:89: rdo ra'i nang du dur khrod kyi 'khor yug bskor zhing /
NK016(ma)007:90: nang gi lha gnas lte ba nas rtsa thig gi
NK016(ma)007:91: bar cha drug tu bgos pa'i dum bu dang po
NK016(ma)007:92: pad+ma'i lte ba mu khyud dang bcas pa /
NK016(ma)007:97: drug pa bzhi bcu mu khyud dang bcas pa ste
NK016(ma)007:98: pad ma 'dab brgya'i dkyil 'khor bya ba rnams ni
NK016(ma)007:99: khyad par ro // de nas tshon lnga mdog rigs sdebs pa /
NK016(ma)007:100: so so'i gnas su h'u s+w+aa +aam h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:101: m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam las de bzhin gshegs pa
NK016(ma)007:102: rigs lnga'i ngo bor gyur pa rnams bdag nyid kyi
NK016(ma)007:103: sku la zhugs / byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba tshon rtsi rnams la thim par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:105: +aahsarba pany+tsa rat+na sa ma ye h'u h'u /
NK016(ma)007:106: zhes ci nus bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK016(ma)007:107: h'u zhes brjod pas rin po che'i rdul phra rab kyi rdul tshon 'bar bar bsam nas /
NK016(ma)007:108: dbus kyi lte ba mthing ga ze'u 'bru ljang gu
NK016(ma)007:109: la 'dab bzhi dkar ser dmar ljang ste phyogs tshon
NK016(ma)007:110: / 'dab brgyad nas 'dab ma bzhi bcu pa'i bar
NK016(ma)007:111: thams cad lha so so'i kha dog gam mdzes tshon
NK016(ma)007:112: / / mu khyud steng gi gdung zlum mtshon byed kyi mthing ga rdo rje'i phreng ba can /
NK016(ma)007:113: 'og gzhi'i sna tshogs rdo rje'i ra phyogs mdog /
NK016(ma)007:114: dur khrod kyi gzhi nag po la de'i chos kyis 'jigs par bkra ba /
NK016(ma)007:115: tshon thob lhag ma sgyu 'phrul zhi ba dang mthun par bya zhing /
NK016(ma)007:116: lha'i gnas rnams su sku'am yig 'bru phyag mtshan nam thig le rnams lha'i kha dog dang /
NK016(ma)007:117: mthun par ji ltar rigs pa dgod /
NK016(ma)007:118: thig tshon gyi las zin pa na ye shes pa mchod nas badz+ra muhs gshegs su gsol /
NK016(ma)007:119: de dag ni dkyil 'khor gyi khang pa rnying par
NK016(ma)007:120: skabs 'ga' zhig tu rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor sgrub
NK016(ma)007:121: bde ba'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:122: bzhi pa bum pa bsham pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:123: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus bum pa nang bcud can mgul
NK016(ma)007:124: chings sogs chas su bcug pa kha rgyan dang bcas
NK016(ma)007:126: lnga pa mchod rdzas bsham pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:127: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha'i nang rim la sman gtor rak+ta
NK016(ma)007:128: mar me ste bskang rdzas rnams brgya yan chad kyi
NK016(ma)007:129: phreng ba / de'i phyi rim la bdug spos /
NK016(ma)007:132: dri chab rnams kyang lha grangs dang mnyam pa'am ji tsam 'byor pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:133: gzhan yang rigs brgya'i gtor zlum mtheb kyus bskor ba
NK016(ma)007:134: dang bka' srung spyi sgos kyi gtor ma dang bcas
NK016(ma)007:135: pa'i g.yas g.yon du sman rag /
NK016(ma)007:136: mkha' 'gro ma gtor ma'i dbang gi zlum gtor rgyan can zhig kyang stegs la bkod /
NK016(ma)007:137: nye 'khor kun tu tshogs kyi yo byad /
NK016(ma)007:140: rgyal mtshan ba dan sogs bkod pas mdzes par brgyan /
NK016(ma)007:141: slob bu gcig dong sprugs 'don du'ang gzhug /
NK016(ma)007:142: gral phyag dang tshul phyag sngon du 'gro bas sgrub
NK016(ma)007:143: pa po thams cad stan la 'dug ste rol mos
NK016(ma)007:145: gnyis pa khyad par gyi sngon 'gro la drug las /
NK016(ma)007:146: dang po rgyud sbyang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:147: bla ma rig 'dzin rgyal ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)007:148: gyi lha tshogs thams cad badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs sad
NK016(ma)007:149: par byas la / bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)007:150: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK016(ma)007:151: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:152: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK016(ma)007:153: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)007:154: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:155: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:156: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK016(ma)007:157: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:158: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK016(ma)007:159: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK016(ma)007:160: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK016(ma)007:161: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)007:162: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK016(ma)007:163: dag pa gsum gyis lus dbul lo //
NK016(ma)007:164: tshe rabs 'grangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK016(ma)007:165: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK016(ma)007:166: zhes lan gsum la sogs pas rgyud dag par byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:167: tshogs zhing rnams rang la bsdus te chos dbyings ka dag gi klong du mnyam par bzhag go //
NK016(ma)007:168: gnyis pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:169: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK016(ma)007:170: bdag nyid skad cig gis rdo rje he ru ka
NK016(ma)007:171: sku mdog mthing nag mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum
NK016(ma)007:172: phyag drug gi / dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu /
NK016(ma)007:173: gnyis pas rtse lnga dang b+hany+tsa /
NK016(ma)007:174: gsum pas zhing dbyug dang 'jig rten 'degs pa'i tshul can /
NK016(ma)007:175: zhabs bzhi g.yas brkyang pa'i dor stabs kyis ru dra pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba mnan pa /
NK016(ma)007:176: yum rdo rje khro mo'i dbang phyug ma sngon mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK016(ma)007:177: g.yon pas dung khrag zhal du stob pa /
NK016(ma)007:182: thod pa skam rlon tshal bu'i dbu rgyan se ral dpung rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK016(ma)007:183: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK016(ma)007:184: smin mtshams su rak+ta'i thig le //
NK016(ma)007:185: mgrin par zhag gi zo ris te dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis spras pa /
NK016(ma)007:186: khyad par yum la gzig gi pags pa'i sham thabs can /
NK016(ma)007:187: shin tu gtum zhing khros pa ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:188: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK016(ma)007:189: ha la ha la ha la h'u /
NK016(ma)007:191: yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas khro boo 'chol
NK016(ma)007:192: pa mtshon cha sna tshogs kyi char 'bebs pa dpag
NK016(ma)007:194: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang /
NK016(ma)007:195: bdud bgegs log par 'dren pa'i tshogs thams cad zil
NK016(ma)007:196: gyis mnan pas thams cad 'jigs shing skrag nas bag
NK016(ma)007:197: 'khums te gnas par gyur pa la /
NK016(ma)007:201: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)007:203: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK016(ma)007:204: sa rba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa
NK016(ma)007:207: khro bo'i tshogs nam mkha' gang ba rnams kyis gsang
NK016(ma)007:208: spyod blta bar mi dbang ba'i bgegs dang log par
NK016(ma)007:209: 'dren pa thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par byas /
NK016(ma)007:212: khro bo'i rang bzhin gyi rdo rje'i gur khang chen
NK016(ma)007:213: por gtams pa'i phyi rol kun nas bskal pa'i me
NK016(ma)007:215: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs 'khrugs pa'i rwa ba gsum rim
NK016(ma)007:216: gyis phyogs kun gang bas mtshams bcad de cis kyang
NK016(ma)007:218: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:219: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs bshags yul rgyal ba zhi khro
NK016(ma)007:220: mkha' khyab tu sad pa'i spyan sngar bshags sdom gyis
NK016(ma)007:223: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK016(ma)007:224: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK016(ma)007:225: thugs rje nyi gsal 'od bzhin snyoms mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)007:226: 'dir gshegs bdag la dgongs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:227: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK016(ma)007:228: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga'i gtso //
NK016(ma)007:229: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol pa'i lha //
NK016(ma)007:230: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:231: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:232: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK016(ma)007:233: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya cher yongs bkod de //
NK016(ma)007:234: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK016(ma)007:235: kun tu bzang mo gsang ba'i b+ha ga la //
NK016(ma)007:236: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus rab 'byams kun //
NK016(ma)007:237: 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa //
NK016(ma)007:238: gnyis med byang chub sems kyis mnyes gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:239: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK016(ma)007:240: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK016(ma)007:241: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:242: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud //
NK016(ma)007:243: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK016(ma)007:244: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK016(ma)007:245: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK016(ma)007:246: 'byung dang 'byung gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK016(ma)007:247: gsang chen rab dgyes gzugs can bdag nyid ma //
NK016(ma)007:248: mkha' dbyings klong yangs pad+mo 'khyil pa la //
NK016(ma)007:249: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal zhing //
NK016(ma)007:250: ma bcos spros med byang chub snying po'i sku //
NK016(ma)007:251: cir yang snang ba bde chen g.yung drung lha //
NK016(ma)007:253: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK016(ma)007:254: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:255: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK016(ma)007:256: rigs lnga dpal chen khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK016(ma)007:257: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK016(ma)007:258: ye shes sprul pa'i lha tshogs mang po dang //
NK016(ma)007:259: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK016(ma)007:260: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod ma //
NK016(ma)007:261: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnal 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:262: dpang gyur rdo rje dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:263: h'u thugs rje gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin bdag cag gis //
NK016(ma)007:264: 'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK016(ma)007:265: bla med go 'phang bgrod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK016(ma)007:266: bstan pa rgya mtsho so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK016(ma)007:267: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor sdom pa'i mchog /
NK016(ma)007:268: rdo rje 'da' dka' dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK016(ma)007:269: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK016(ma)007:270: snga phyir nos shing gnyer du smras so 'tshal //
NK016(ma)007:271: yun du mi gtong 'da' bar mi bgyid cing //
NK016(ma)007:272: don las gol zhig ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK016(ma)007:273: gdod bya long yod snyam pa'i le lo yis //
NK016(ma)007:274: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:275: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med dbang gyur te //
NK016(ma)007:276: sgom la mi brtson bsnyen sgrub g.yel la sogs //
NK016(ma)007:277: tshor dang ma tshor ma rig dbang gis na //
NK016(ma)007:278: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK016(ma)007:279: rnal 'byor gang zhig dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK016(ma)007:280: skad cig tsam yang 'phrad par mi bya zhes //
NK016(ma)007:281: bka' las byung zhing de ltar ma lcogs te //
NK016(ma)007:282: gsang sgo 'chol bas dbye bsal dka' pa dang //
NK016(ma)007:283: mngon shes med pas skyon can ma rtogs te //
NK016(ma)007:284: nyams dang tshogs 'dres nyams pa bskang ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:285: nyams dang snod min rnams la chos bshad dang //
NK016(ma)007:286: nyams la mi 'dzem nyams pa'i skyon la sogs //
NK016(ma)007:287: nyams dang 'grogs shing nyams pa de dag gi //
NK016(ma)007:288: nyams grib skyon gyis gos par gyur to 'tshal //
NK016(ma)007:289: tshe 'di'i rkyen dang yun gyis sgrib gyur rnams //
NK016(ma)007:290: rab gnong 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK016(ma)007:291: byams pa'i thugs brtses bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK016(ma)007:292: gnyis med dbyings las mi 'gyur bdag bkod de //
NK016(ma)007:293: dmigs med btang snyoms ngang la bzhugs nas kyang //
NK016(ma)007:294: gnyis med don gyi tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:295: don dam dmigs med spros las 'das pas na //
NK016(ma)007:296: rnam rtog gang yang dmigs par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK016(ma)007:297: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi dbang gis na //
NK016(ma)007:298: nongs par mchis na rab gnong bzod par gsol //
NK016(ma)007:299: zhes pas sdig sgrib thams cad ye nas rang bzhin med pa'i dbyings su dag par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:300: bzhi pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:301: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgya snying gar bcings te lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK016(ma)007:302: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK016(ma)007:303: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rjes dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK016(ma)007:304: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gyur gcig pu pa //
NK016(ma)007:305: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:306: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK016(ma)007:307: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK016(ma)007:308: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK016(ma)007:309: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:310: bdag ni rgyal srid mtho ris longs spyod dang //
NK016(ma)007:311: 'dod pa'i yon tan bdag sgrub ma lags te //
NK016(ma)007:312: 'gro la snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //
NK016(ma)007:313: 'di la kun mkhyen khyod ni dpang du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:314: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK016(ma)007:315: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK016(ma)007:316: 'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pa //
NK016(ma)007:317: sun par mi bgyi mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK016(ma)007:318: snying nas bdag ni khe dang grags la sogs //
NK016(ma)007:319: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK016(ma)007:320: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag ste //
NK016(ma)007:321: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyad //
NK016(ma)007:322: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK016(ma)007:323: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK016(ma)007:324: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK016(ma)007:325: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:326: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK016(ma)007:327: dum bu stong du bdag gi lus gtub kyang //
NK016(ma)007:328: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK016(ma)007:329: yi dam rgyal ba khyed ni yongs mi spong //
NK016(ma)007:330: rdo rje'i dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni /
NK016(ma)007:331: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK016(ma)007:332: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la zhugs pa rnams //
NK016(ma)007:333: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ci nus bsrung //
NK016(ma)007:334: 'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la //
NK016(ma)007:335: bdag ni 'jigs pa ci yang ma mchis te //
NK016(ma)007:336: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK016(ma)007:337: phyi mthar thug gi bar du gnas par spro //
NK016(ma)007:338: gzhan don 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK016(ma)007:339: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis spyad //
NK016(ma)007:340: 'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK016(ma)007:341: rang dbang du ni skye ba blang bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:342: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK016(ma)007:343: mya ngan 'das la spro ba ma mchis te //
NK016(ma)007:344: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK016(ma)007:345: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:346: srid par yun ring dus su brtson pa ni //
NK016(ma)007:347: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags pas na //
NK016(ma)007:348: ji srid ngan song stongs par ma gyur pa //
NK016(ma)007:349: de srid bdag gis skyo ba'i sems mi bskyed //
NK016(ma)007:350: shes rab thabs kyi 'gro ba'i don bgyid pa //
NK016(ma)007:351: snying rje'i longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK016(ma)007:352: sems dmyal yi dwags gshin rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK016(ma)007:353: lha yi dga' tshal lta bur blta bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:354: 'gro la thugs rje dpal gyi mgur nas gsungs //
NK016(ma)007:355: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK016(ma)007:356: bdag gis 'jig rten thug par ma mchis par //
NK016(ma)007:357: ji ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:358: srid par las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK016(ma)007:359: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK016(ma)007:360: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK016(ma)007:361: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK016(ma)007:362: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK016(ma)007:363: sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK016(ma)007:364: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyis //
NK016(ma)007:365: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskang //
NK016(ma)007:366: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur pa //
NK016(ma)007:367: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK016(ma)007:368: bdag gis zhi dang khro bo'i phrin las kyis //
NK016(ma)007:369: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par gzhom par bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:370: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK016(ma)007:371: rdo rje rgyal po khyod la brten nas ni //
NK016(ma)007:372: sangs rgyas zhing sbyang 'gro la sman slad du //
NK016(ma)007:373: byang chub snying po bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:374: bdag ni 'phags mchog phyag rgyar mngon sprul te //
NK016(ma)007:375: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK016(ma)007:376: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK016(ma)007:377: khyed kyi zhabs kyi drung du mchi bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)007:378: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK016(ma)007:379: dmyal sogs me dpung zhi bar bgyid la sogs //
NK016(ma)007:380: sems can don la myur du bdag mchi na //
NK016(ma)007:381: dam pa rnams nus kyis mthu stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:383: ye shes kyi 'khor lo thams cad mkha' khyab tu sad par byas te /
NK016(ma)007:384: h'u a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)007:385: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK016(ma)007:386: khyad pa'i bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK016(ma)007:387: mthu rtsal dbyung pa'i dus la bab //
NK016(ma)007:388: byin gyis rlob pa'i dus la bab //
NK016(ma)007:389: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK016(ma)007:390: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK016(ma)007:392: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK016(ma)007:393: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK016(ma)007:394: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK016(ma)007:395: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:396: spos sreg cing rol mo sna tshogs kyi sgra sbyar te /
NK016(ma)007:397: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes bsdus pas /
NK016(ma)007:398: mkha' khyab kyi lha tshogs thams cad bdag gnas yo
NK016(ma)007:399: byad rnams la thim ste sku gsung thugs mi zad
NK016(ma)007:400: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor byin gyis brlab par bsam
NK016(ma)007:401: mo / drug pa mchod rdzas byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:403: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ais bsang /
NK016(ma)007:404: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aas sbyangs /
NK016(ma)007:405: stong pa'i ngang las rang nyid rdor sems su gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h'u las a /
NK016(ma)007:411: nam mkha'i khams thams cad khyab /
NK016(ma)007:413: 'khor 'das kyi rtsi bcud thams cad bsdus nas mchod rdzas rnams la thim par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:414: na mahs man+ta bud+h+aa n+aam ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:415: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK016(ma)007:418: bde mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen po'i rol pa las /
NK016(ma)007:419: rdo rje zhabs bsil ma la sogs pa mchod pa'i lha mo khrus gzhong dang /
NK016(ma)007:420: spos khang man+d+ha ra'i me tog la sogs pa thogs
NK016(ma)007:421: pa nam mkha' gang ba rnams su gyur par bsam
NK016(ma)007:425: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum chad /
NK016(ma)007:426: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK016(ma)007:427: bdud rtsi'i snod gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'i dbus
NK016(ma)007:428: su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar mi sha
NK016(ma)007:430: shar du ba lang gi sha dang dri chen /
NK016(ma)007:431: lhor khyi sha dang sha chen /
NK016(ma)007:432: nub tu rta sha dang rak+ta /
NK016(ma)007:433: byang du glang po che'i sha dang dri chu rnams kyi steng du rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)007:438: h+aa t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:441: 'od zer 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur ba las /
NK016(ma)007:447: so so'i rigs kyi dril bu rnams su gyur /
NK016(ma)007:450: dbus su mi bskyod pa yab yum mthing ga /
NK016(ma)007:453: shar du rnam snang yab yum dkar po /
NK016(ma)007:456: lhor rin 'byung yab yum ser po /
NK016(ma)007:459: nub tu snang mtha' yab yum dmar po /
NK016(ma)007:462: byang du don grub yab yum ljang khu rnams su gyur /
NK016(ma)007:464: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK016(ma)007:466: dzah h+aum bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta /
NK016(ma)007:469: rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyi sbyor bas zhu
NK016(ma)007:470: ba las byung ba'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi gyis
NK016(ma)007:471: mtshan pa'i kha gcod rdo rje rgya gram gyi lte
NK016(ma)007:472: bar / pad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha ha ya gri wa h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:473: rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma dang rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin pa lte ba yan chad thon pa /
NK016(ma)007:475: shar du mi pham ma dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:476: lhor khro gnyer ma ser mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:477: nub tu ro langs ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:478: byang du ral gcig ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:479: gyi 'od zer gyis 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi thams cad bkug /
NK016(ma)007:480: dam tshig ni bdud rtsi dang gnyis su med par
NK016(ma)007:481: gyur pa las ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho
NK016(ma)007:482: chen por gyur par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:483: g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyi rdo rjes bdud rtsi la reg ste /
NK016(ma)007:484: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK016(ma)007:485: zhes brgya rtsa tsam bzlas shing mthar g.yon bskor du dkrugs te /
NK016(ma)007:488: yum bzhi bdud rtsi la thim par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:490: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum pad+ma ba lim ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+r+aum /
NK016(ma)007:491: gtor gzhong pad+ma'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang
NK016(ma)007:492: du gtor rdzas 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma tshang
NK016(ma)007:493: ba med pa la gyis mtshan par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:496: ba lim ta te dz+wa ba lim ta ba la b+aa d+y+aa gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:498: gzugs rdo rje ma la sogs lha mo nam mkha'
NK016(ma)007:499: gang bas 'dod yon dpag tu med par spro ba'i
NK016(ma)007:500: bdag nyid du gyur par bsam /
NK016(ma)007:502: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum b+hany+dza ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK016(ma)007:503: dmar gyi dung chen yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang
NK016(ma)007:504: du rak+ta la ra yig dmar pos mtshan par gyur
NK016(ma)007:507: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK016(ma)007:508: chags med rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrug pas nam mkha' gang bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:510: khyad par gyi sbyor ba sems bskyed pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:511: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos gnyis /
NK016(ma)007:516: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)007:517: ye shes sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK016(ma)007:518: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK016(ma)007:519: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)007:521: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)007:522: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)007:523: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK016(ma)007:524: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK016(ma)007:525: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)007:526: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)007:529: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)007:530: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun kyi gsang //
NK016(ma)007:531: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK016(ma)007:532: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK016(ma)007:533: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)007:534: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)007:535: dmigs pa med pas thams cad dmigs //
NK016(ma)007:536: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK016(ma)007:537: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyis chos //
NK016(ma)007:538: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)007:541: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos la /
NK016(ma)007:542: sdig sgrib sbyong ba'i rim pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:543: tshogs bsag pa'i rim pa gnyis /
NK016(ma)007:545: ting nge 'dzin gyis khog dbub pa /
NK016(ma)007:546: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK016(ma)007:547: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis med du bya ba /
NK016(ma)007:548: sdig sgrib sbyong ba'i las la sbyar ba'o //
NK016(ma)007:551: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK016(ma)007:552: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK016(ma)007:553: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK016(ma)007:554: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:555: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad mi dmigs shing
NK016(ma)007:556: spros pa dang bral ba stong pa nyid du bsgom
NK016(ma)007:558: de bzhin nyid ni spros med kyang //
NK016(ma)007:559: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK016(ma)007:560: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK016(ma)007:561: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK016(ma)007:562: de bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK016(ma)007:563: sems can rnams la 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK016(ma)007:564: snying rje chen po mkha' khyab tu bsgom pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:566: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK016(ma)007:568: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK016(ma)007:569: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK016(ma)007:570: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK016(ma)007:571: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK016(ma)007:572: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK016(ma)007:574: rang rig snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin a dkar po'i rnam par bsgom pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:576: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:577: brten pa lha bsgom pa gnyis las /
NK016(ma)007:579: sems nyid a dkar po dri ma med par gsal ba las /
NK016(ma)007:580: e yam wam lam sum ram rnams chad /
NK016(ma)007:584: e las nam mkha' chos kyi 'byung gnas 'byams klas pa'i dbyings su /
NK016(ma)007:585: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu g.yo ba'i ba dan gyis mtshan pa /
NK016(ma)007:586: wam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum po /
NK016(ma)007:587: lam las sa'i dkyil 'khor ser po gru bzhi /
NK016(ma)007:588: sum las rin po che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin gyi ri rab zur bzhi pa /
NK016(ma)007:589: ram las me'i khor yug nam mkha'i mkha' klas par 'bar ba'o //
NK016(ma)007:590: ri rab kyi steng du rgyu'i a las b+h+r+aum chad /
NK016(ma)007:593: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+dala b+h+r+aum /
NK016(ma)007:594: b+h+r+aum yig yongs su gyur pa las ye shes rin
NK016(ma)007:595: po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo
NK016(ma)007:596: bzhi pa / nang nas rim pa bzhin mthing dkar
NK016(ma)007:597: ser dmar ljang ba'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang
NK016(ma)007:599: rin po che'i pha gu ser po rin po che
NK016(ma)007:600: sna tshogs pas bkra ba 'phyar thabs su bkod pa'i
NK016(ma)007:601: mthar mu tig gi mgul 'khor 'phyang ba /
NK016(ma)007:602: de'i steng du bre phul gyi snam bu la gser
NK016(ma)007:603: gyi ska rags bzhi'i phyi ngos su ma ka ra'i
NK016(ma)007:604: kha nas rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang dra ba
NK016(ma)007:605: phyed pa / dar dang rnga yab /
NK016(ma)007:607: zla ba rlung gis bskyod pa la sogs pas mdzes pa /
NK016(ma)007:608: de'i phyi ngos su bya 'dab las 'phyang ba'i rin po che'i shar bu /
NK016(ma)007:609: steng ngos su mda' yab pad+ma 'dab ma phyed pa'i dbyibs can /
NK016(ma)007:610: de dag gi bar bar du bum pa la gnas pa'i rgyal mtshan dang /
NK016(ma)007:612: zur bzhir rnam par bkra ba'i gdugs kyis brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)007:613: rtsig pa'i 'gram nas 'dod yon gyi snam bu dmar
NK016(ma)007:614: pos bskor ba la gzugs rdo rje ma sogs lha
NK016(ma)007:615: mo rnams kyis mchod pa'i sprin rab 'byams spro ba
NK016(ma)007:616: / sgo dang sgo khyud kyi mtshams dang zur bzhir
NK016(ma)007:617: zla ba phyed pa la gnas pa'i rdo rje nor
NK016(ma)007:618: / bus brgyan pa / sgo logs kyi phyi zur
NK016(ma)007:619: bzhi nas bum pa la gnas pa'i ka ba bzhi
NK016(ma)007:620: bzhis btegs pa'i rta babs snam bu brgyad pa bsil
NK016(ma)007:621: khang dang ldan pa'i rtse mor pad+ma la gnas pa'i
NK016(ma)007:622: chos kyi 'khor lo gdugs kyis phub pa g.yas g.yon
NK016(ma)007:623: du ri dwags pho mo dang bcas pa /
NK016(ma)007:626: ba dan sna tshogs pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:627: gser gyi dril bu la sogs pas brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)007:628: sgo'i g.yas g.yon gyi gzhi la t+aa la'i ljon pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:629: dpag bsam gyi shing la bkra shis pa'i bya snyan par sgrog pa sna tshogs gnas pa /
NK016(ma)007:630: shing de dag kyang gser gyi tha gus bres shing
NK016(ma)007:631: dril bu dang g.yer kha chos kyi sgra snyan par
NK016(ma)007:633: yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i khrus kyi rdzing bu la lha mo sna tshogs bde bar rtse ba /
NK016(ma)007:634: rin po che'i phung po 'od 'bar ba re re ste brgyad dang /
NK016(ma)007:635: gzhan yang rin po che sna bdun dang /
NK016(ma)007:636: bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad sogs 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad kyis mdzes par byas pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:637: gzhal yas khang gi nang bar khyams gru bzhi pa
NK016(ma)007:638: gru chad dang bcas pas bskor ba'i phyogs bzhi nas
NK016(ma)007:639: rigs kyi mtshan ma can gyi ka ba gnyis gnyis
NK016(ma)007:640: te brgyad kyis btegs pa'i rdo rje'i gdung zlum dang
NK016(ma)007:641: / gdung chen bzhis mig mang ris su bris pas
NK016(ma)007:642: mdzes par phub pa'i dbus phyur bur rtse mo rdo
NK016(ma)007:643: rje rin po che'i tog gis mdzes pa /
NK016(ma)007:648: dbus sngo ba dwangs shing sgrib pa med par kun
NK016(ma)007:649: tu gsal ba sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba la
NK016(ma)007:650: rdzogs pa / de'i phyi rol du rdo rje bsrung
NK016(ma)007:651: ba'i gur khang 'bar ba me'i 'od zer kun tu
NK016(ma)007:653: gzhal yas khang gi dbus su seng ge brgyad kyis
NK016(ma)007:654: btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri bkod pa phul du
NK016(ma)007:659: pad nyi zla ba'i gdan cha shas yongs su rdzogs par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:660: gnyis pa brten pa lha bsgom pa la /
NK016(ma)007:665: rang gi sems nyid a dkar po dri ma med
NK016(ma)007:666: par gsal ba zla ba'i gdan gyi steng du babs
NK016(ma)007:667: / de yongs su gyur pa las h'u yig mthing ga ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'bar ba /
NK016(ma)007:675: rdo rje de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)007:676: rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog mthing ka /
NK016(ma)007:677: mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi /
NK016(ma)007:678: g.yas dang po rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin cing /
NK016(ma)007:679: g.yon dang po dril bu dkur brten pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK016(ma)007:680: bar pa gnyis 'khor lo dang rin po che /
NK016(ma)007:681: tha ma gnyis kyis pad+ma dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:682: dbu skra ral pa'i thor tshugs can /
NK016(ma)007:683: zhabs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:684: yab kyi thugs ka nas m+aum chad /
NK016(ma)007:692: yab kyi g.yon phyogs nye ba'i 'phang du yum rdo
NK016(ma)007:693: rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma sngon mo phyag g.yas
NK016(ma)007:694: dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK016(ma)007:695: g.yon rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:696: brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba /
NK016(ma)007:697: gnyis ka'ang lha rdzas kyi dar dkar po gser gyi ngang ris can gyi stod g.yogs dang /
NK016(ma)007:699: kha dog sna tshogs pa'i cod pan /
NK016(ma)007:701: gar gyi phu dung ste dar gyi chas gos lnga dang /
NK016(ma)007:708: phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu ste rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis mdzes par spras pa /
NK016(ma)007:709: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can gsal 'tsher lhun
NK016(ma)007:710: sdug gzi byin ldan pa ste zhi ba'i nyams dgus
NK016(ma)007:711: rgyas pa / sangs rgyas kyi sprin phung mtha' yas
NK016(ma)007:712: par 'char ba'i 'od zer kha dog drug gi snang
NK016(ma)007:713: ba re re yang bye ba phrag drug drug tu
NK016(ma)007:714: 'phro zhing 'bar ba'i klong na bde stong gnyis su
NK016(ma)007:715: med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:716: rang nyid gzhi lus kyi rdor sems yab yum du gsal ba'i yab kyi gtsug tor gyi rtse la /
NK016(ma)007:718: rnam snang dkar po g.yas 'khor lo thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)007:719: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:721: kun tu bzang po mthing ga mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK016(ma)007:724: rin 'byung ser po g.yas rin po che thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)007:725: rkang pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:727: don grub ljang gu g.yas rgya gram thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)007:730: snang mtha' dmar po g.yas pad+ma thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)007:731: kun tu bzang po rdo rje'i skyil mo krung dang /
NK016(ma)007:732: gzhan rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:733: mig gi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:735: sa snying dkar po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:737: mee d+h+aa ra ni s+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:738: byams pa dkar ser g.yas klu shing dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:739: rna ba'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:741: phyag rdor mthing ga g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:743: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:744: sgrib sel dmar ser g.yas glegs bam dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:747: nam snying ser po g.yas ral gri dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:749: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:750: kun bzang dmar ljang g.yas rin po che'i snye ma dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:751: lce'i 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:752: h+r+ai h+aa h+aum pad+ma pra da ma /
NK016(ma)007:753: spyan ras gzigs dmar po g.yas pad+ma dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:755: m+aum sh+r+ai am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:756: 'jam dpal dkar ljang g.yas u t+pal dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:757: brgyad ka'ang g.yas brkyang ba'i phyed skyil gyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:759: h+aum ya m+aan+ta kri ta phata /
NK016(ma)007:760: gshin rje gshed smug nag n+ri mgo gdengs pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:763: stobs po che ser nag rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:766: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:769: rta mgrin dmar nag thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:770: bzhi ka'ang g.yas brkyang ba'i gyad kyi 'dor stabs su bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:773: lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wam 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:775: mu ne h+aum t+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:776: lha min gyi thub pa mthing ga go cha 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:779: mi'i thub pa ser po gseg par 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:782: byol song gi thub pa dmar nag pusti 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:785: yi dwags kyi thub pa ser nag rin po che'i sgrom bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:788: dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:789: drug ka'ang 'gro ba'i don la bzhengs stabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:790: yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'i gtsug tor gyi rtse la /
NK016(ma)007:792: spyan ma dkar mo g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon 'khor lo thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:793: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:794: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ah kun
NK016(ma)007:795: tu bzang mo mthing ga thal mo thugs kar sbyar
NK016(ma)007:798: m+aa ma k+ai ser mo g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon rin po che thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:799: rkang pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:801: dam tshig sgrol ma ljang gu g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon rgya gram thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:804: gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon pad+ma thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:805: kun tu bzang mo pad+ma'i skyil mo krung dang /
NK016(ma)007:806: bzhan rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:807: mig gi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:808: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)007:809: sgeg mo dkar mo khu tshur gyi rgyas me long bsnams pa g.yon gyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:811: spos ma dkar ser spos khang bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:812: rna ba'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:813: t+r+aam m+aa le sa ma ya hoh phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba snams pa /
NK016(ma)007:816: me tog ma dmar ser me tog gi phreng ba bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:818: h+r+aim g+ai t+ai r+aa go ham /
NK016(ma)007:819: glu ma dmar mo pi wam bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:821: bam d+ai ba su gi r+ai /
NK016(ma)007:822: mar me ma dmar ljang mar me snams pa /
NK016(ma)007:823: lce'i 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK016(ma)007:824: am nirte r+aa ga ya mye /
NK016(ma)007:825: gar ma ljang gu gar rgya mdzad pa /
NK016(ma)007:828: dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung phor bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:829: brgyad ka'ang g.yon brkyang ba'i phyed skyil gyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:831: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:832: lcags kyu ma smug nag lcags kyu 'dzin pa //
NK016(ma)007:834: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:835: zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:837: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:838: dril bu ma ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:840: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:841: lcags sgrog ma dmar nag lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:842: bzhi ka'ang g.yon brkyang ba'i gyad kyi 'dor stabs su bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)007:845: kun bzang yab yum rnams zhi ba'i rgyan chas bcu gsum gyis mdzes shing /
NK016(ma)007:846: tshul dgu'i nyams kyi rgyas pa /
NK016(ma)007:847: thugs pa drug mchog gi sprul sku'i cha byad dang /
NK016(ma)007:848: mthar byed yab yum khro gtum mi bzad pa'i nyams can dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas dang ldan pa /
NK016(ma)007:849: thams cad kyang rdo rje sems dpa' snang stong sgyu
NK016(ma)007:850: 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rang bzhin gyi sku gsung thugs mi
NK016(ma)007:851: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor rnam par dag pa'o
NK016(ma)007:852: // de ltar gsal ba'i lha tshogs thams cad kyi
NK016(ma)007:853: srog gi gor rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa'
NK016(ma)007:854: rgyan dang phyag mtshan spangs pa re re'i thugs kar
NK016(ma)007:855: so so'i sa bon gyis mtshan par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:856: gnyis pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:857: lha thams cad kyi spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK016(ma)007:858: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)007:859: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)007:861: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:862: yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:863: nga rgyal bya zhing rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor gtugs te /
NK016(ma)007:864: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa sa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:865: mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aam dmar po /
NK016(ma)007:866: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)007:867: gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)007:869: de gzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:870: +aam yongs su gyur pa las snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:871: rdo rje'i phyag rgya mgrin par sarba ta th+aa ga
NK016(ma)007:872: ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma
NK016(ma)007:873: ko&a ham / snying gar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum sngon po /
NK016(ma)007:874: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)007:875: thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)007:877: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:878: h+aum yongs su gyur pa las mi bskyod pa sngon
NK016(ma)007:879: po rdo rje 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam la
NK016(ma)007:880: / rdo rje'i phyag rgya snying gar sarba ta th+aa
NK016(ma)007:881: ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma
NK016(ma)007:882: / ko&a ham / zhes sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum du nga rgyal bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:883: gsum pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:884: lha thams cad kyi thugs ka'i sa bon rnams las
NK016(ma)007:885: 'od zer 'phros pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar
NK016(ma)007:886: gshegs pa thams cad dbang gi lha rigs lnga yab
NK016(ma)007:887: yum gyi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs
NK016(ma)007:888: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu
NK016(ma)007:889: r+aa ga na badz+ra s+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK016(ma)007:891: de rnams gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad /
NK016(ma)007:892: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu
NK016(ma)007:893: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang bskur bar
NK016(ma)007:894: bsam zhing / rdo rje phyi bsdams las gung mo gnyis brkyang ba spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK016(ma)007:895: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:896: de bzhin du mdzub mo brkyang ba dpral bar /
NK016(ma)007:897: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:898: srin lag brkyang ba rna ltag g.yas par /
NK016(ma)007:899: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:900: mthe bong brkyang ba ltag par /
NK016(ma)007:901: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aut+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:902: mathe'u chung brkyang ba rna ltag g.yon par /
NK016(ma)007:903: ma h+aa kri t+ya nush+th+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:904: zhes dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK016(ma)007:905: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas bsgyur /
NK016(ma)007:906: chu'i lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK016(ma)007:907: pa las mi bskyod pa bdag por gyur pa'i rigs
NK016(ma)007:908: lnga sprul sku'i cha byad can gyi dbu brgyan par
NK016(ma)007:910: phung po lnga dag pa rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su nga rgyal bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:912: rnam grangs spros pa sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa'i skabs 'dir yang /
NK016(ma)007:913: dkyil 'khor spros pa'i skabs ltar bskur ba nyid byin
NK016(ma)007:914: rlabs kyi sngon du mdzad par snang na'ang 'thad par
NK016(ma)007:915: ma mthong ste / sku gsung thugs kyi lha rgya
NK016(ma)007:916: nyi shu la'ang dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga ma
NK016(ma)007:917: bsgoms na rtsa lha yab yum gnyis la yan lag
NK016(ma)007:918: gi lha stong bsgom par gsungs pa'i grangs 'jig pa'i
NK016(ma)007:919: ma mthong ste / phyir ro // gsum par rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis med du /
NK016(ma)007:921: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:922: gzhi lus kyi ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar dwangs
NK016(ma)007:923: ma'i srog h'u mthing ga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin
NK016(ma)007:925: de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bskul bas /
NK016(ma)007:926: chos sku 'gyur ba med pa'i ngang las gzugs sku
NK016(ma)007:927: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor chen por
NK016(ma)007:929: lag gnyis lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas pas /
NK016(ma)007:931: stong pa shin tu yod med rnal 'byor mthus //
NK016(ma)007:932: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gnas //
NK016(ma)007:933: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs mdzad dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:934: rdo rje sems dpa' khyod bdag bskal bzang dpal //
NK016(ma)007:935: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aa na ma ha k+aa
NK016(ma)007:936: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam
NK016(ma)007:937: / gnyis pa spyan drangs pa ni //
NK016(ma)007:938: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK016(ma)007:939: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK016(ma)007:940: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nya gnas bskyod la //
NK016(ma)007:941: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK016(ma)007:942: dam tshig pa'i thugs ka nas spros pa'i dzahh+aum bam
NK016(ma)007:943: hohs ye shes pa dgug bcings bsdams la dgyes pa
NK016(ma)007:944: bskyed nas / dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dab 'byor du bzhugs par bsam mo /
NK016(ma)007:945: gsum pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:948: h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK016(ma)007:949: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK016(ma)007:950: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:951: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor bas /
NK016(ma)007:952: dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa gnyis kyi sku
NK016(ma)007:953: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnam gnyis su med
NK016(ma)007:955: bzhi pa dngos grub bskul te bstim pa ni //
NK016(ma)007:956: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)007:957: yon tan phyin las rmad po che //
NK016(ma)007:958: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)007:959: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK016(ma)007:962: badz+ra sa ma hoh zhes dngos grub bskul nas /
NK016(ma)007:963: dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa phyag rgya bzhis dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor
NK016(ma)007:964: lo chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin dbyer med du
NK016(ma)007:966: bzhi pa sdig sgrib sbyong pa'i las la sbyar ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:967: gzhi lus kyi ye shes sems dpa'i thugs ka'i dwangs
NK016(ma)007:968: ma'i srog h'u yig zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnas
NK016(ma)007:969: pa'i mthar g.yas bskor du rigs brgya'i rang bzhin gyis
NK016(ma)007:970: yi ge brgya pa kha dog dkar po 'od 'bar
NK016(ma)007:972: de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis tshom bu stong gi lha tshogs thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)007:973: sku'i cha thams cad las byung ba'i byang chub sems
NK016(ma)007:974: kyi rang bzhin gyi 'od zer dmigs yul gtso bor
NK016(ma)007:975: gyur pa'i sems can thams cad la phog pas /
NK016(ma)007:976: bag chags dang bcas pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa dang sdug bsngal thams cad dang /
NK016(ma)007:977: khyad par na ra ka la sogs pa'i ngan song
NK016(ma)007:978: ngan 'gro log par ltung ba'i chos can gyi sdug
NK016(ma)007:979: bsngal rgyu dang bcas pa thams cad dong nas sprugs
NK016(ma)007:980: te / rang bzhin rdo rje sems dpar gnas pa mngon du gyur pa'i go 'phang bkod /
NK016(ma)007:981: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs dang ro gcig tu gyur /
NK016(ma)007:983: 'od zer de rnams slar 'dus te rang la thim
NK016(ma)007:984: pas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs mi
NK016(ma)007:985: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bdag nyid du lhag
NK016(ma)007:987: badz+ra sa t+wa sogs yig brgya'i 'dzab dang /
NK016(ma)007:988: bo b+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa
NK016(ma)007:989: tu +aah zhes zhi ba spyi sngags kyang bzla zhing
NK016(ma)007:990: dgos pa khyad par can gyi slad du spro na
NK016(ma)007:992: da ha da ha sogs ngan song sbyong pa'i sngags sbril ba'ang cung zad re bazla'o //
NK016(ma)007:994: thugs ka'i h+aum gi 'od zer gyis reg pas dag
NK016(ma)007:995: pa'i snod bcud thams cad 'od du zhu nas rdor
NK016(ma)007:996: sems tshom bu stong gi lha tshogs dang bcas pa
NK016(ma)007:997: la thim / de thams cad ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK016(ma)007:998: de dwangs ma'i srog h+aum la /
NK016(ma)007:999: de gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du thim nas mi dmigs pa'i ngang la nyams par bzhags cing /
NK016(ma)007:1000: slar yang thun mtshams kyi lhar ldang bar bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:1001: gnyis pa tshogs bsags pa'i rim la la /
NK016(ma)007:1003: tshogs bsags pa dngos gnyis dang po la /
NK016(ma)007:1004: ting nge 'dzin rnam gsum bsgom pa tshogs rten gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK016(ma)007:1005: rang bzhin gyi dkyil dang gnyis med du bya ba'o //
NK016(ma)007:1008: de gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du thim /
NK016(ma)007:1009: zhes mi rtog pa de'i ngang las /
NK016(ma)007:1010: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK016(ma)007:1012: rang rig snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin
NK016(ma)007:1013: a dkar po'i rnam par bsgom pa'i bar gong bzhin
NK016(ma)007:1015: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK016(ma)007:1016: dbang don gyi dkyil 'khor sprul pa /
NK016(ma)007:1017: thun mong du dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1019: dang po rten gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1020: sems nyid a dkar po dri ma med par gsal ba las /
NK016(ma)007:1022: 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad kyis mdzes par gang ba'o //
NK016(ma)007:1023: zhes pa'i bar gong bzhin las /
NK016(ma)007:1024: nang gi phyogs bzhi nas rigs kyi mtshan ma can gyi ka ba gnyis gnyis te /
NK016(ma)007:1026: sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba la rdzogs pa /
NK016(ma)007:1027: de'i phyi rol du r+au dra longs spyod dang bcas
NK016(ma)007:1028: pa dbyings su bsgral ba'i dur khrod chen po brgyad
NK016(ma)007:1029: / dur khrod kyi chos rnams kyis 'jigs par byas
NK016(ma)007:1030: pa'i phyi nas rdo rje bsrung ba'i gur khang 'bar
NK016(ma)007:1031: ba me'i 'od zer kun tu 'phro bas yongs su
NK016(ma)007:1032: / bskor ba'o // gzhal yas khang gi dbus su /
NK016(ma)007:1034: kha dog sna tshogs pa'i pad+ma 'dab ma brgya pa'i 'khor lo /
NK016(ma)007:1036: thub pa drug dang dbang mo nyer brgyad ma gtogs
NK016(ma)007:1037: pa'i lha'i gnas thams cad du nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)007:1038: re re / a tsan+d+ra man+da la /
NK016(ma)007:1041: sgo skyong bzhi rnams kyi gnas ma gtogs pa'i nyi
NK016(ma)007:1042: gdan thams cad kyi steng du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)007:1043: re re gsal bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:1044: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1045: rang gi sems nyid a yig dkar po dri ma
NK016(ma)007:1046: med pa zla ba ltar gsal ba las rigs brgya'i
NK016(ma)007:1047: rang bzhin gyi yi ge'i sprin phyungs nas pad+ma'i lte
NK016(ma)007:1048: ba nas brtsams te rim bzhin g.yas bskor du 'khod
NK016(ma)007:1049: pa ni / gtso bo'i gnas pad+ma'i lte ba'i gdan la /
NK016(ma)007:1051: dz+ra sa t+wa sa 'dab ma brgyad la /
NK016(ma)007:1052: ma ya ma nu p+aa la ya ba /
NK016(ma)007:1054: dz+ra sa t+wa t+wa no pa ti sha tha dri d+ho me b+ha wa su to sh+yo /
NK016(ma)007:1056: me b+ha wa su po sh+yo me b+ha wa a
NK016(ma)007:1057: nu raka to me b+ha wa sar ba sid d+hi
NK016(ma)007:1058: me pra yahtsa sar ba kar ma su tsa me
NK016(ma)007:1061: ha ha ha ha hoh b+ha ga w+aan sara ba
NK016(ma)007:1062: ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra m+aa me munya tsa badz+ri
NK016(ma)007:1063: b+ha wa ma h+aa sa ma ya sa t+aa +aahh+au
NK016(ma)007:1064: phatah ces mu tig gi phreng ba lta bur gsal
NK016(ma)007:1066: a zhes brjod pas gzhi'i a de 'od du zhu
NK016(ma)007:1067: nas yig 'bru rnams la khyab par thim pas shin
NK016(ma)007:1071: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK016(ma)007:1073: slar 'dus nas yig 'bru rnams la thim pa 'od
NK016(ma)007:1074: du zhu ba las zhi khro rigs brgya'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)007:1077: rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bcom ldan 'das
NK016(ma)007:1078: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog mthing ga mthing
NK016(ma)007:1079: dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi /
NK016(ma)007:1081: zhabs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1084: yab kyi g.yon phyogs nye ba'i phang du yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma /
NK016(ma)007:1086: bde stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1088: de'i phyi rol gyi 'dab ma bzhi la /
NK016(ma)007:1090: shar du mi bskyod pa sngon po g.yas rdo rje
NK016(ma)007:1091: thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa
NK016(ma)007:1093: lhor rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma sngon mo
NK016(ma)007:1094: g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon rdo rje thugs
NK016(ma)007:1095: kar 'dzin pa / h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta /
NK016(ma)007:1096: nub tu kun tu bzang po mthing ga mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK016(ma)007:1097: a a a badz+ri b+ha dra sa man+ta ah byang
NK016(ma)007:1098: du kun tu bzang mo mthing ga thal mo thugs
NK016(ma)007:1099: kar sbyar ba'o // de'i phyi rol gyi 'dab ma brgyad la shar nas rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)007:1101: rnam snang dkar po g.yas 'khor lo thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)007:1102: l+aam dwe sha ra tih spyan ma dkar mo g.yas
NK016(ma)007:1103: dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon 'khor lo thugs kar
NK016(ma)007:1105: rin 'byung ser po g.yas rin chen thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)007:1107: m+aa ma k+ai ser mo g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon rin chen thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1109: snang mtha' dmar po g.yas pad+ma thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)007:1111: gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon pad+ma thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1113: don grub ljang gu g.yas rgya gram thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)007:1115: dam tshig sgrol ma ljang khu g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon rgya gram thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1116: rigs lnga yab rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung dang yum rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung /
NK016(ma)007:1117: kun tu bzang po rdo rje'i skyil krung dang bzang mo pad+ma'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)007:1118: thams cad kyang rgyan dang cha lugs gtso bo dang mtshungs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1119: de'i phyi rol gyi 'dab ma bcu drug la /
NK016(ma)007:1121: sa snying dkar po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1122: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)007:1123: sgeg mo dkar mo khu tshur gyi rgyas me long bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:1125: nam snying ser po g.yas ral gri dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1126: t+r+aam m+aa le sa ma ya hoh phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:1127: h+r+aim h+aa h'u pad+ma pra da ma /
NK016(ma)007:1128: spyan ras gzigs dmar po g.yas pad+ma dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1129: hri g+ai t+ai ra go ham /
NK016(ma)007:1130: glu ma dmar mo pi wam bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:1132: phyag rdor mthing ga g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1134: gar ma ljang gu gar rgya mdzad pa /
NK016(ma)007:1135: mee d+h+aa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:1136: byams pa dkar ser g.yas klu shing dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1138: spos ma dkar ser spos khang bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:1139: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:1140: sgrib sel dmar ser g.yas glegs bam dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1142: me tog ma dmar ser me tog gi phreng ba bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:1143: h+aum s+w+aa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:1144: kun bzang dmar ljang g.yas rin po che'i snye ma dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1145: bam d+ai pa su gi r+ai /
NK016(ma)007:1146: mar me ma dmar ljang mar me bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)007:1147: m+aum sh+r+ai am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:1148: 'jam dpal dkar ljang g.yas ut+pala dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1150: dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung phor bsnams pa ste /
NK016(ma)007:1151: yab rnams g.yas brkyang ba'i phyed skyil dang /
NK016(ma)007:1152: yum rnams g.yon brkyang ba'i phyed skyil gyis bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)007:1153: thams cad kyang dar gyi na bza' dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1154: de'i phyi rol gyi 'dab ma so gnyis la /
NK016(ma)007:1156: gshin rje gshed smug nag n+ri mgo gdengs pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1157: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:1158: lcags kyu ma smug nag lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1160: stobs po che ser nag rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1161: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:1162: zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1164: rta mgrin dmar nag thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1165: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:1166: lcags sgrog ma dmar nag lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1168: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1169: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+au phata /
NK016(ma)007:1170: dril bu ma ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1171: thams cad kyang khro gtum mi bzad pa'i nyams can gyad kyi dor stabs su bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1173: lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wam 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1174: mu ne h+aum t+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:1175: lha min gyi thub pa mthing ga go cha 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1177: mi'i thub pa ser po gseg par 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1179: byol song gi thub pa dmar nag pusti 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1181: yi dwags kyi thub pa ser nag rin po che'i sgrom bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1183: dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1184: thams cad kyang mchog gi sprul sku'i cha byad can 'gro ba'i don la bzhengs stabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1185: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK016(ma)007:1186: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK016(ma)007:1187: h+aum h+au phata / rdo rje khrag 'thung mthing nag
NK016(ma)007:1188: mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK016(ma)007:1189: po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu
NK016(ma)007:1190: h+aum h+au phata / / lhag ma g.yas gnyis rtse lnga dang ti ra /
NK016(ma)007:1191: g.yon gnyis dung dmar dang 'jig rten /
NK016(ma)007:1192: zhabs bzhi r+au tra pho mo'i gdan la rol pa /
NK016(ma)007:1193: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+au phata /
NK016(ma)007:1194: rdo rje khrag 'thung ma sngon mo g.yas dril bu dang g.yon dung dmar stob pa /
NK016(ma)007:1195: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK016(ma)007:1196: ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da
NK016(ma)007:1197: ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:1198: sangs rgyas khrag 'thung smug nag smug ljang ser ba'i
NK016(ma)007:1199: zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis 'khor lo
NK016(ma)007:1200: dang dril bu / lhag ma g.yas gnyis rdo rje dang ti ra /
NK016(ma)007:1201: g.yon gnyis dung dmar dang kha t+w+aam ka /
NK016(ma)007:1202: zhabs bzhi dri za pho mo'i gdan la rol pa /
NK016(ma)007:1203: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai sarba dush+t+aan+ta h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:1204: sangs rgyas khrag 'thung ma smug nag g.yas dril bu dang g.yon dung dmar stob pa /
NK016(ma)007:1205: rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK016(ma)007:1206: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK016(ma)007:1207: h+aum h+aum phata / rin chen khrag 'thung ser nag
NK016(ma)007:1208: ser smug dmar pa'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK016(ma)007:1209: po gnyis rin po che dang dril bu /
NK016(ma)007:1210: lhag ma g.yas gnyis rdo rje dang ti ra /
NK016(ma)007:1211: g.yon gnyis dung dmar dang dgra s+t+wa /
NK016(ma)007:1212: zhabs bzhi gshin rje'i gdan la rol pa /
NK016(ma)007:1213: ma h+aa s+aur+ya rat+na ma ha kro d+he shwa r+ai bi da ma h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:1214: rin chen khrag 'thung ma ser nag g.yas dril bu dang g.yon dung dmar stob pa /
NK016(ma)007:1215: pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK016(ma)007:1216: barba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK016(ma)007:1217: h+aum h+aum phata / pad+ma khrag 'thung dmar nag dmar
NK016(ma)007:1218: ser ljang ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po
NK016(ma)007:1220: lhag ma g.yas gnyis rdo rje dang ti ra /
NK016(ma)007:1221: g.yon gnyis dung dmar dang rnge'u chung /
NK016(ma)007:1222: zhabs bzhi klu dbang gi gdan la rol pa /
NK016(ma)007:1223: h+r+ai sh+au ta sa ma ta pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai kh+aa hi h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:1224: pad+ma khrag 'thung ma dmar nag g.yas dril bu dang g.yon dung dmar stob pa /
NK016(ma)007:1225: karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK016(ma)007:1226: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK016(ma)007:1227: h+aum h+aum phata / las kyi khrag 'thung ljang nag
NK016(ma)007:1228: ljang dmar smug pa'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK016(ma)007:1229: po gnyis rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK016(ma)007:1230: lhag ma g.yas gnyis rdo rje dang ti ra /
NK016(ma)007:1231: g.yon gnyis dung dmar dang thong gshol /
NK016(ma)007:1232: zhabs bzhi gnod sbyin gyi gdan la rol pa /
NK016(ma)007:1233: sarba a mo g+ha ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai bi shwa h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:1234: las kyi khrag 'thung ma ljang nag g.yas dril bu dang g.yon dung dmar stob pa /
NK016(ma)007:1235: yab rnams zhabs g.yas brkyang dang yum rnams g.yon brkyang ba'i dor stabs kyi tshul can /
NK016(ma)007:1236: thams cad kyang gar dgu'i ros sgeg cing dur khrod rol pa'i chas kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1237: badz+ra goo r+ai hah goo r+ai sngon mo g.yas zhing dbyug dang g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1238: badz+ra tsoo r+ai hah tsoo r+ai ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK016(ma)007:1239: badz+ra pra mo he hah pra mo dmar mo chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'phyar pa /
NK016(ma)007:1240: badz+ra bee ta li hah bee ta l+ai nag mo rdo rje dang zhing chung 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1241: badz+ra puk+ka s+ai hah puk+ka s+ai dmar ser zhing chung gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK016(ma)007:1242: badz+ra g+hasma r+ai hah g+hasma r+ai ljang khu g.yon gyi dung khrag g.yas pa'i rdo rjes dkrug pa /
NK016(ma)007:1243: badz+ra sma sha n+ai hah sma sha mthing nag byis pa'i ro bzung bas snying za ba /
NK016(ma)007:1244: badz+ra tsan+da l+ai hah tsan+da l+ai ser skya zhing chung gi mgo lus 'dral ba /
NK016(ma)007:1245: thams cad kyang gcer bu lang tshos sgeg cing khro
NK016(ma)007:1246: 'dzum bzhad pa dur khrod rol pa'i chas can g.yon
NK016(ma)007:1247: brkyang ba'i stabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1248: de'i phyi rol gyi 'dab ma bzhi bcu la /
NK016(ma)007:1250: seng gdong ser mo ro za zhing lag gnyis thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK016(ma)007:1251: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)007:1252: stag gdong ma dmar mo lag gnyis mthur du bsnol bas ro bzung ba /
NK016(ma)007:1253: badz+ra sh+ri g+aa la mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)007:1254: wa gdong ma nag mo zhing chung lces ldag pa /
NK016(ma)007:1255: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)007:1256: spyang gdong ma mthing nag zhing chung gi khog pa 'dral ba ste mche ba can bzhi /
NK016(ma)007:1257: badz+ra gri d+d+ha mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)007:1258: rgod gdong ma dmar mo zhing gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK016(ma)007:1260: kang+ka'i gdong ma dmar skya bam ro phrag par 'khur ba /
NK016(ma)007:1261: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)007:1262: bya rog gdong can nag mo ral gri dang b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1263: badz+ra u l+au ka mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)007:1264: 'ug gdong ma mthing nag rdo rje'i dbyug pa 'dzin pa ste gshog pa can bzhi'o //
NK016(ma)007:1265: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah rta gdong ma sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1267: phag gdong ma nag mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1269: seng gdong ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1270: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hoh spyang gdong ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1271: thams cad kyang gcer bu rang rang khros pa'i zhal can dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas dang ldan pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1278: srin mo dmar ser g.yag gdong tri shul 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1279: tshangs ma dmar skya sbrul gdong rdo rje rtse lnga 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1280: 'khrug mo ser nag gzig gdong dbyug to dang sdigs mdzub /
NK016(ma)007:1281: brgya byin ma dkar dmar sre mong mgo can thod khrag 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1282: khyab 'jug ser mo pha wam mgo can 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1283: dbang mo dmar skya dred gdong bam dbyug 'dzin pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1290: zhi ba dmar mo dom mgo can rgyu zhags 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1291: bdud rtsi ma sngon mo chu srin mgo can bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1292: zhi ba ma sngo skya sdig pa'i mgo can pun+da ri ka 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1293: be con ma nag mo khra mgo can thod rlon 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1294: srin mo dmar nag wa gdong rgyu zhags 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1295: za byed nag mo stag mgo bam chen 'dzin pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1298: e ka tsa ri ni b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)007:1302: dga' byed dmar mo rgod gdong khog chen 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1303: khrag 'thung ma dmar nag rta gdong rdo rje'i dbyug pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1304: gcig spyod ma dkar dmar khyung gdong b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1305: 'dod pa dmar ser khyi gdong byis bam 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1306: nor srung dkar dmar pra shud mgo can pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1307: rlung mo dmar skya sha ba'i mgo can ba dan 'dzin pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1308: ma h+aa m+aa ra na badz+ra b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)007:1314: gsod byed ma ljang nag spyang gdong rnge'u chung 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1315: me mo dmar ser skyin gdong me sgron 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1316: phag mo ljang ser phag gdong mche ba 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1317: rgan byed ljang sngon khwa ta'i mgo can dung khrag 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1318: sna chen ljang dmar ba lang mgo can bam chen 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1319: chu lha ma ljang nag sbrul gdong bdud rtsi'i thod pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1320: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa li b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)007:1324: nag mo chen mo khu byug mgo can lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1325: rdo rje ra mo sngon mo ra gdong rgyu zhags 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1326: bum sna ma dmar mo seng gdong lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1327: gsus 'dzin ma ljang nag skya ka'i mgo can dril
NK016(ma)007:1328: bu 'dzin pa thams cad kyang drag mo'i gzugs can
NK016(ma)007:1329: dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas kyis brgyan te zhing gi
NK016(ma)007:1331: gzhan yang dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyi'i 'khor yug la
NK016(ma)007:1332: sprul pa dang yang sprul bka' sdod dam can rgya
NK016(ma)007:1333: mtsho'i tshogs mtha' yas pa dang bcas pa rnams kyang
NK016(ma)007:1334: rang rang gi rgyan dang cha lugs dang ldan cing
NK016(ma)007:1335: so so'i 'khor gyis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor
NK016(ma)007:1336: lo nyi ma dang 'od zer gyi tshul du mngon
NK016(ma)007:1337: par snang ba'i sgyu 'phrul gyi rol mo bsam gyis
NK016(ma)007:1338: mi khyab pa dam tshig gi 'khor lor rdzogs par
NK016(ma)007:1339: bsam mo // gnyis pa dbang don gyi dkyil 'khor sprul pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1340: gtso bo rdor sems su gsal ba'i thugs ka nas b+h+r+au yig chad de bum pa'i nang du song /
NK016(ma)007:1343: bum pa rin po che'i rang bzhin yangs shing rgya che ba /
NK016(ma)007:1349: lha'i gos kyis mgul bcings pa /
NK016(ma)007:1350: dpag bsam shing gi kha rgyan can /
NK016(ma)007:1351: nang chu dang bcud sna tshogs kyis yongs su gang ba'i nang du /
NK016(ma)007:1352: 'khor loo ser po rtsibs bzhi pa sgo bzhi glo
NK016(ma)007:1353: 'bur gyi tshul du gnas pa'i dbus su seng ge
NK016(ma)007:1357: byang du shang shang gis btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri /
NK016(ma)007:1358: sna tshogs pad+ma dang nyi zla brtsegs pa'i gdan lnga'i steng du /
NK016(ma)007:1359: slar yang gi rang gi thugs ka nas /
NK016(ma)007:1372: so so'i rigs kyi dril bu rnams dang bcas par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:1377: dbus su mi bskyod pa sngon po rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1378: dbyings phyug ma sngon mo rdo rjes mtshan pa'i dril
NK016(ma)007:1379: bu dang rdo rje 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor
NK016(ma)007:1382: shar du rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1383: spyan ma dkar mo 'khor lo'i dril bu dang 'khor lo 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK016(ma)007:1386: lhor rin 'byung ser po rin po che dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1387: m+aa ma k+ai ser mo rin po che'i dril bu
NK016(ma)007:1388: dang rin po che 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor
NK016(ma)007:1391: nub tu snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1392: gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma'i dril bu dang pad+ma 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK016(ma)007:1395: byang du don grub ljang gu ral gri dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1396: dam tshig sgrol ma ljang gu ral gri'i dril bu dang ral gri 'dzin pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:1398: yab rnams mnyam pa'i skyil krung dang yum rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis rol pa /
NK016(ma)007:1399: zhi ba'i rgyan chas bcu gsum gyis mdzes shing tshul dgus brjid pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:1400: gsum pa dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1401: de ltar gsal ba'i tshogs rten dang bum pa'i lha
NK016(ma)007:1402: thams cad kyi srog gi gor rang 'dra ba'i ye
NK016(ma)007:1403: shes sems dpa' rgyan dang phyag mtshan spangs pa re
NK016(ma)007:1404: re'i thugs kar so so'i sa bon gyis mtshan par
NK016(ma)007:1405: bsam la / sa bon rnams las 'od zer 'phros
NK016(ma)007:1406: pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams
NK016(ma)007:1407: cad dbang gi lha rigs lnga yab yum gyi rnam
NK016(ma)007:1408: par badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)007:1409: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:1411: de rnams gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad pa /
NK016(ma)007:1412: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu
NK016(ma)007:1413: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang baskurabasa nyon
NK016(ma)007:1414: mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK016(ma)007:1415: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas bsgyur /
NK016(ma)007:1416: chu'i lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK016(ma)007:1417: pa las rang rigs bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga
NK016(ma)007:1418: sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu rgyan par mos
NK016(ma)007:1419: la / phung po lnga dag pa rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su nga rgyal bya /
NK016(ma)007:1420: rigs lnga so so'i dbang rgya sngar ltar bcings pa
NK016(ma)007:1421: gnas so sor 'jog cing dbang sngags brjod pa ste
NK016(ma)007:1422: / de'ang rigs gang yin gyi sngags dang por brjod cing phyag rgya spyi bo'i gnas su 'jog la /
NK016(ma)007:1423: gang dbus su song ba'i sngags rgya dang rigs bdag
NK016(ma)007:1424: gi shul du mi bskyod pa spo ba nges par
NK016(ma)007:1425: byas nas / mi bskyod pa'i dbang rgya dang sh+au nya t+aa dang por byas pa'i sngags tshan lngas /
NK016(ma)007:1429: rdo rje khrag 'thung rnams yum dang bcas pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:1430: thub pa drug la mi bskyod pa bdag por gyur
NK016(ma)007:1431: pa'i rigs lnga'i cod pan gyis dbu brgyan par gyur
NK016(ma)007:1432: / rnam snang gi dbang rgya dang a dar+sha dang por brjod pas sngags tshan lngas /
NK016(ma)007:1437: sangs rgyas khrag 'thung rnams yum dang bcas pa la
NK016(ma)007:1438: rnam snang bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga'i cod pan
NK016(ma)007:1440: de bzhin du sa ma t+aa dang por /
NK016(ma)007:1445: rin chen khrag 'thung rnams yum dang bcas pa la
NK016(ma)007:1446: rin 'byung bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga'i cod pan
NK016(ma)007:1453: pad+ma khrag 'thung rnams yum dang bcas pa la snang
NK016(ma)007:1454: mtha' bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga'i cod pan gyis
NK016(ma)007:1461: las kyi khrag 'thung rnams yum dang bcas pa la
NK016(ma)007:1462: don grub bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga'i cod pan
NK016(ma)007:1464: de nas rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya dang sh+au nya t+aa'i sngags brjod pas /
NK016(ma)007:1465: gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu dang /
NK016(ma)007:1466: dbang mo nyer brgyad la dbang bskur bas spyi bor
NK016(ma)007:1467: rdo rje rtse lnga pa re res dbu brgyan par
NK016(ma)007:1468: bsam mo // byin gyis barloba pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1469: lha thams cad kyi spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i zhes sogs nas /
NK016(ma)007:1470: tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:1471: zhes pa'i bar sngar bzhin no //
NK016(ma)007:1472: gsum pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis med du bya ba la bzhi las /
NK016(ma)007:1473: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1474: rang gi thugs kar dwangs ma'i srog yig ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin rtag tu 'char bzhin pa /
NK016(ma)007:1476: gzugs sku zhi khro rab 'byams rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor chen por sad par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:1477: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK016(ma)007:1479: stong pa shin tu zhes sogs nas /
NK016(ma)007:1480: sa ma ya s+t+wam gyi bar ro //
NK016(ma)007:1481: gnyis pa spyan drang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:1483: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK016(ma)007:1484: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK016(ma)007:1485: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK016(ma)007:1486: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK016(ma)007:1487: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)007:1488: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK016(ma)007:1489: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK016(ma)007:1490: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK016(ma)007:1491: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK016(ma)007:1492: zhes pas dam tshig gi 'khor lo dang nye bar spyan drangs te //
NK016(ma)007:1493: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK016(ma)007:1495: me ri 'dab 'byor du bzhugs par bsam pa'i bar sngar bzhin no //
NK016(ma)007:1496: gsum pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:1499: sa ma ya h+aa'i bar dang /
NK016(ma)007:1500: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK016(ma)007:1502: dam tshig pa dang zhes sogs nas /
NK016(ma)007:1503: gnyis su med par rig par bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:1505: bzhi pa dngos grub bskul te bstim pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1506: ye shes rgyal po zhes sogs nas /
NK016(ma)007:1507: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh'i bar dang /
NK016(ma)007:1508: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)007:1509: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:1510: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK016(ma)007:1511: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK016(ma)007:1512: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)007:1513: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK016(ma)007:1514: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya hoh zhes dngos grub
NK016(ma)007:1515: bskul bas ye shes kyi 'khor lo dang gnyis med
NK016(ma)007:1516: du dgyes pa bskyed pa las drin lan gyi tshul
NK016(ma)007:1518: a li u li t+aa li ta b+aa li damsh+ta
NK016(ma)007:1519: go n+aa ro tri kha ram yo gi n+ai kh+aa
NK016(ma)007:1521: dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum ha he phata /
NK016(ma)007:1522: zhes brjod pas dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo chu la
NK016(ma)007:1523: chu bzhag pa bzhin dbyer med du gyur nas gsal
NK016(ma)007:1525: gnyis pa tshogs bsags pa dngos la /
NK016(ma)007:1534: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i thugs ka nas mar me
NK016(ma)007:1535: gcig las gnyis chad kyi tshul du rang nyid gtso
NK016(ma)007:1536: bo gnyis pa'i rnam pas thon nas dkyil 'khor gyi
NK016(ma)007:1538: sems can thams cad dang bya byed thun mong par
NK016(ma)007:1539: gyur nas phyag dang mchod pa sogs las kyi rim
NK016(ma)007:1541: lus zhing rdul dang mnyam par sprul nas /
NK016(ma)007:1542: bla ma mnyam med sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK016(ma)007:1543: dus gsum bde gshegs sras bcas thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)007:1544: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin byin brlabs pa //
NK016(ma)007:1545: bka' drin chen po'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1546: zhes rtsa ba'i bla ma la phyag byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:1548: kun bzang phyag rdor ku ku r+aa dza che //
NK016(ma)007:1549: in+d+ra b+hu ti sh+aakya pu tri'i zhabs //
NK016(ma)007:1550: sing+ha r+aa dza u pa r+aa dza la //
NK016(ma)007:1551: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)007:1552: go ma de bi rdo rje h+aum mdzad rtsal //
NK016(ma)007:1553: sangs rgyas gsang ba bi ma la mi tra //
NK016(ma)007:1554: gnyags lo gzhon nu sog po lha dpal la //
NK016(ma)007:1555: sgo gsum gus pas gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes sru legs sgron //
NK016(ma)007:1556: sras mchog gzhon snying zhu ston bsod nams mtshan //
NK016(ma)007:1557: bde gshegs zur chen zur chung shes rab grags //
NK016(ma)007:1558: sgo gsum gus pas sgrol chen bsam rdor thugs sras sangs rin zhabs //
NK016(ma)007:1559: 'gos lo gzhon dpal bsod nams rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK016(ma)007:1560: se ston rin rgyan rgya hor rdo rje rtsal //
NK016(ma)007:1561: sgo gsum gus pas pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal bdud 'joms rje //
NK016(ma)007:1562: tshe ring dbang po ngag dbang phun tshogs mtshan //
NK016(ma)007:1563: brgyud srol kun 'dus rig 'dzin gter bdag gling //
NK016(ma)007:1564: sgo gsum gus pas lo chen chos dpal rgyal sras rin rnam zhabs //
NK016(ma)007:1565: pad+ma bstan 'dzin phrin las rnam par rgyal //
NK016(ma)007:1566: phrin las chos sgron sangs rgyas kun dag'i dpal //
NK016(ma)007:1567: sgo gsum gus pas bstan 'dzin nor bu phan bde'i 'od zer 'bar //
NK016(ma)007:1568: khyab bdag drin chen rtsa brgyud bla ma dang //
NK016(ma)007:1569: rab 'byams zhi khro dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i lhar //
NK016(ma)007:1570: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)007:1571: zhes brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs kyi tshigs rkang bzhi pa bsgyur pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:1572: gzhan yang brgyud tshul du ma yod pa las gang mos pa de dang der bsgyur bas chog go //
NK016(ma)007:1574: mi rtog rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK016(ma)007:1575: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK016(ma)007:1576: thugs rje'i bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK016(ma)007:1577: rdo rje sems dpa' che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1578: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas lhun grub pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:1579: bya ba byed dang yid chos rnam par dag /
NK016(ma)007:1580: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la phyag 'tshal lo //
