NK016(ma)007:1581: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK016(ma)007:1582: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK016(ma)007:1583: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:1584: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1585: ngo mtshar pho brang bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK016(ma)007:1586: dus gsum sras bcas thams cad bskyed mdzad ma //
NK016(ma)007:1587: rigs kyi yum gyur rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1588: rnam shes dbang po dag pas thugs dang gsung //
NK016(ma)007:1589: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi sras mchog ste //
NK016(ma)007:1590: sems dpa' chen po brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1591: sgeg mo phreng thogs rin chen glu gar can //
NK016(ma)007:1592: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i mchod pas rgyal ba mchod //
NK016(ma)007:1593: byang chub lha mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1594: bdug pa me tog mar me dri chab ma //
NK016(ma)007:1595: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams la mchod 'bul ma //
NK016(ma)007:1596: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams la phyag batshala lo //
NK016(ma)007:1597: drag shul thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dul mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)007:1598: tshad med bzhi ldan sgo bzhi thub par srung //
NK016(ma)007:1599: mthar byed sgo ba bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1600: rtag chad lta 'byin gsang ba yum gyi ngang //
NK016(ma)007:1601: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril 'khrol ma //
NK016(ma)007:1602: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1603: steng 'og phyogs bzhi 'jig rten 'dul ba'i gtso //
NK016(ma)007:1604: nyon mongs drug 'joms rgyud drug dag par sbyong //
NK016(ma)007:1605: bcom ldan thub pa drug la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1606: 'jig rten 'das pa'i dus su sngon byung ba //
NK016(ma)007:1607: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK016(ma)007:1608: dpal chen khrag 'thung rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1609: khro mo dbang phyug sku la 'khril mdzad cing //
NK016(ma)007:1610: mkha' 'gro mi bzad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ma //
NK016(ma)007:1611: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum rnams la phyag 'tshal //
NK016(ma)007:1612: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK016(ma)007:1613: ye shes sku mchog 'jigs byed slas su bzhugs //
NK016(ma)007:1614: khro mo chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1615: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK016(ma)007:1616: 'dod dgur bsgyur pa'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK016(ma)007:1617: phra men chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1618: rdo rje gdong mo pho nya mgyogs ma bzhi //
NK016(ma)007:1619: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi thub par bsrung //
NK016(ma)007:1620: sgo skyong khro mo bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1621: dpal gyi 'khor tshogs badz+ra +aa ra l+ai //
NK016(ma)007:1622: mkha' la shugs 'gro ma tshogs dbang phyug ma //
NK016(ma)007:1623: rnal 'byor nyi shu brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1624: phyogs bcu dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan steng na //
NK016(ma)007:1625: ye shes bskal pa me dpung 'bar ba'i klong //
NK016(ma)007:1626: bdud 'dul yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1627: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1628: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1629: cir yang sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshol lo //
NK016(ma)007:1630: mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1631: mngon par byang chub sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1632: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyis bsgrubs pa yis //
NK016(ma)007:1633: tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing yon tan mthar phyin pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:1634: sku dang ye shes tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1635: a ti pu hoh pra ti pu hoh zhes pa tsam mam /
NK016(ma)007:1636: 'grub tu rung na phyag gi bkol byang rgyas pa bzhin ci nus su bya ba gal che'o //
NK016(ma)007:1637: gnyis pa mchod pa la bcu bzhi las /
NK016(ma)007:1638: dang po phyag rgya'i mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1639: lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK016(ma)007:1640: de rnams kyi steng du h'u s+w+aa +aam h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:1641: g.yon gyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK016(ma)007:1642: de dag gi steng du m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:1643: lnga gnyis zung du sprad pa las //
NK016(ma)007:1644: sbyar bas phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK016(ma)007:1645: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te //
NK016(ma)007:1646: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK016(ma)007:1647: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK016(ma)007:1648: bde ba chen po spyin pa'i rgya //
NK016(ma)007:1650: zhes pas phyag rgya mdun du bsgyur nas g.yon du dgrol /
NK016(ma)007:1651: de'i tshe lha gsal ba phyag chen /
NK016(ma)007:1655: de nas khro bo'i tshogs kyi sku gsung thugs mi
NK016(ma)007:1656: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i nga rgyal byas la
NK016(ma)007:1657: / khrag 'thung rgyal po gar la dgyes //
NK016(ma)007:1658: sku mdog zhal ni rnam par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)007:1659: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu ba'i //
NK016(ma)007:1660: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK016(ma)007:1662: spro na rngams glog dang he ru ka 'dus par
NK016(ma)007:1663: gsung pa'i phyag rgya rnams las dkyil 'khor 'di'i lha
NK016(ma)007:1664: grangs dang mtshungs pa tsam sbyar na shin tu'ang skabs
NK016(ma)007:1667: nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK016(ma)007:1669: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK016(ma)007:1670: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK016(ma)007:1671: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK016(ma)007:1672: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK016(ma)007:1673: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK016(ma)007:1674: khe b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam
NK016(ma)007:1675: ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:1677: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK016(ma)007:1678: 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK016(ma)007:1679: phyag dang zhabs ni bsil nas kyang //
NK016(ma)007:1680: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:1681: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra
NK016(ma)007:1682: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga
NK016(ma)007:1683: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:1685: so so'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK016(ma)007:1687: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa ma //
NK016(ma)007:1689: byams pa thabs dang shes rab las //
NK016(ma)007:1690: badz+ra d+h+au pe'i mchod par rol //
NK016(ma)007:1691: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK016(ma)007:1693: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)007:1695: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)007:1696: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK016(ma)007:1697: u t+pal mthing ga me tog 'thor //
NK016(ma)007:1699: snying rje thabs dang shes rab las //
NK016(ma)007:1701: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK016(ma)007:1703: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si d+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)007:1705: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)007:1706: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK016(ma)007:1707: dbang gi phyag na sgron ma bsnams //
NK016(ma)007:1709: dga' ba thabs dang shes rab las //
NK016(ma)007:1710: badz+ra lo ke'i mchod par rol //
NK016(ma)007:1711: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK016(ma)007:1713: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)007:1715: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)007:1716: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke h+r+aih tsan+dana bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs ma //
NK016(ma)007:1718: btang snyoms thabs dang shes rab las //
NK016(ma)007:1720: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK016(ma)007:1722: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)007:1724: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)007:1725: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK016(ma)007:1726: lha mo rnams kyis dkyil 'khor ba rnams mchod nas
NK016(ma)007:1727: shangs la sogs pa'i dbang po so so la thim
NK016(ma)007:1729: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:1730: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:1731: mchod chen thams cad dag cing lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:1733: lha mo rnams slar byung ste rang gi gnas bzhir
NK016(ma)007:1734: thim par sku gsung thugs phrin las bzhi'i dngos grub
NK016(ma)007:1738: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK016(ma)007:1739: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK016(ma)007:1740: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK016(ma)007:1741: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK016(ma)007:1742: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK016(ma)007:1743: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba //
NK016(ma)007:1744: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi sman //
NK016(ma)007:1745: thams cad bdud rtsi'i rnal 'byor che //
NK016(ma)007:1746: bde gshegs zhi ba'i thugs dam nyid //
NK016(ma)007:1747: khro bo rgya mtshos dngos grub mchog /
NK016(ma)007:1749: bdag cag dad pas 'bul gyis bzhes //
NK016(ma)007:1750: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:1753: kun bzang phyag rdor ku ku r+aa dza che //
NK016(ma)007:1754: in+d+ra b+hu ti sh+aakya pu tri'i zhabs //
NK016(ma)007:1755: sid+ha r+aa dza u pa r+aa dza la //
NK016(ma)007:1756: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)007:1757: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:1758: go ma de bi rdo rje h+aum mdzad rtsal //
NK016(ma)007:1759: sangs rgyas gsang ba bi ma la mi tra //
NK016(ma)007:1760: gnyags lo gzhon nu sog po lha dpal la //
NK016(ma)007:1761: sman mchod 'bul lo sarba ta th+aa gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes sru legs sgron //
NK016(ma)007:1762: sras mchog gzhon snying zhu ston bsod nams mtshan //
NK016(ma)007:1763: bde gshegs zur chen zur chung shes rab grags //
NK016(ma)007:1764: sman mchod sarba glan dang 'gar ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan dpal //
NK016(ma)007:1765: rdor 'od bsod nams rgyal mtshan chos seng zhabs //
NK016(ma)007:1766: sangs rgyas dpal ba bsod nams mgon po la //
NK016(ma)007:1767: sman mchod sarba sgrol chen bsam rdor thugs sras sangs rin zhabs //
NK016(ma)007:1768: 'gos lo gzhon dpal bsod nam rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK016(ma)007:1769: se ston rin rgyan rgya hor rdo rje rtsal //
NK016(ma)007:1770: sman mchod sarba pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal bdud 'joms rje //
NK016(ma)007:1771: tshe ring dbang po ngag dbang phun tshogs mtshan //
NK016(ma)007:1772: brgyud srol kun 'dus rig 'dzin gter bdag gling //
NK016(ma)007:1773: sman mchod sarba lo chen chos dpal rgyal sras rin rnam zhabs //
NK016(ma)007:1774: pad+ma bstan 'dzin phrin las rnam par rgyal //
NK016(ma)007:1775: phrin las chos sgron sangs rgyas kun dag'i dpal //
NK016(ma)007:1776: sman mchod sarba bstan 'dzin nor bu phan bde'i 'od zer 'bar //
NK016(ma)007:1777: khyab bdag drin chen rtsa brgyud bla ma dang //
NK016(ma)007:1778: rab 'byams zhi khro dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i lhar //
NK016(ma)007:1779: sman mchod sarba zhes bsgyur ba sogs ji ltar rigs pas phul la /
NK016(ma)007:1780: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK016(ma)007:1781: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:1782: 'gro ba'i don mdzad sprul sku thub drug la //
NK016(ma)007:1783: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)007:1784: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK016(ma)007:1785: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khro rgyal yab yum dang //
NK016(ma)007:1786: gnas yul phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi rnams la //
NK016(ma)007:1787: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub bstsol //
NK016(ma)007:1788: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:1789: ma lhar byams shing sring ltar rab gdung ma //
NK016(ma)007:1790: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:1791: ma tshogs dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK016(ma)007:1792: sman mchod sarba dpa' bo mkha' 'gro dam can srung ma'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:1793: zhing skyong gzhi bdag rigs drug pha ma sogs //
NK016(ma)007:1794: srid gsum ka dag rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK016(ma)007:1795: sman mchod sarba ta th+aa ga ta zhes gu h+ya
NK016(ma)007:1796: lag gi phyag rgyas gtor bas ye shes kyi bdud
NK016(ma)007:1797: rtsi'i zegs ma'i sprin las bdud rtsi'i char babs pas
NK016(ma)007:1798: dkyil 'khor pa thams cad mnyes shing tshim par bsam
NK016(ma)007:1799: la / mthar dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:1800: rang gi lce la h+aum yig dang /
NK016(ma)007:1801: sman gyi steng du 'bru gsum bsgoms te /
NK016(ma)007:1803: rdo rje lce yi dam tshig la //
NK016(ma)007:1804: rdo rje can gyi 'bru gsum bsgom //
NK016(ma)007:1805: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NK016(ma)007:1806: myang na dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)007:1807: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK016(ma)007:1810: zhes rim par blangs te lce la bzhag pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:1811: drug pa bdud rtsi gsang bsnan gyi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1812: bdud rtsi'i rgyun b+hany+dzara lan gsum du sbreng zhing /
NK016(ma)007:1814: mi bskyod ye shes bde ba'i mchog dang ldan pa'i rol la bsnams su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:1815: a la la hoh byang chub sems dpa'i bde mchog de nyid 'gog pa rnams las bslang ba'i phyir //
NK016(ma)007:1816: chags pa med pa'i bde mchog kun tu myong mdzad bzhes shing bsnams su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:1818: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde la rol zhing dam bcas 'jig rten sgrol //
NK016(ma)007:1819: byang chub skye gnas bde mchog dbyings las mi nyams dga' ba'i gar mdzod cig /
NK016(ma)007:1820: a la la hoh zhen cing chags pa'i mtha' la nyon mongs rno skams gzir ba yis //
NK016(ma)007:1821: myong byed bde mchog brgyad dang ldan pas thabs kyi sku la smre par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:1822: 'gro kun tshangs par spyod pa'i byang chub sgo mor lam gtod cig /
NK016(ma)007:1823: bde mchog bdud rtsi khyad par med pa'i tshogs la bka' stsol cig /
NK016(ma)007:1824: a la la hoh zhes pas dang pos lha rnams dgyes pa bskyed /
NK016(ma)007:1825: gnyis pas nyan thos rnams 'gog pa las bslang /
NK016(ma)007:1826: gsum pas rgyal sras rnams gzhan don la bskul bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:1827: bdun pa rak+ta'i mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1829: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK016(ma)007:1830: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi rang bzhin du //
NK016(ma)007:1831: khams gsum dug gsum bsgral ba'i rak+ta mchog /
NK016(ma)007:1832: zhi khro rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK016(ma)007:1833: khams gsum zil gnon dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:1834: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:1835: badz+ra kro d+ha man+da la ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram h+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:1836: brgyad pa gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1838: chos dbyings rnam dag gtor gzhong rgya chen du //
NK016(ma)007:1839: gtor ma ye shes snang ba rgya mtshor 'khyil //
NK016(ma)007:1840: dkar dmar thig le bdud rtsi'i rol mtshor spel //
NK016(ma)007:1841: 'dod yon lha mo'i sprin gyis brgyan pa 'di //
NK016(ma)007:1842: zhi khro rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs la 'bul /
NK016(ma)007:1843: +aahh+aum su ra te u pa b+h+yah ka ma la
NK016(ma)007:1844: m+aa la badz+ra a mri ta ha ra na pra
NK016(ma)007:1845: t+aits+tsha b+ha ga w+aan dzahh+aum bam hoh a la la
NK016(ma)007:1846: hoh zhes dang / badz+ra kro d+ha man+da la ma
NK016(ma)007:1847: h+aa ba lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi
NK016(ma)007:1848: hoh zhes dang / / zhes lan gsum gyis phul
NK016(ma)007:1849: bas 'dod yon drug gi lha mo mkha' khyab tu
NK016(ma)007:1850: spros pa dkyil 'khor ba rnams kyi dbang po drug
NK016(ma)007:1851: gi gnas su thim pas dgyes shing tshim par byas
NK016(ma)007:1852: nas gnyis med du gyur par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:1853: dgu pa yid byung gi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1854: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK016(ma)007:1855: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK016(ma)007:1856: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK016(ma)007:1857: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:1858: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK016(ma)007:1859: mdzes par bres shing spras pa dang //
NK016(ma)007:1861: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK016(ma)007:1862: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK016(ma)007:1863: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK016(ma)007:1864: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK016(ma)007:1865: bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK016(ma)007:1866: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK016(ma)007:1867: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK016(ma)007:1868: rang la mdzes par ba rgyan pa yi //
NK016(ma)007:1869: lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyis //
NK016(ma)007:1870: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK016(ma)007:1871: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK016(ma)007:1872: dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par dbul //
NK016(ma)007:1873: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK016(ma)007:1874: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK016(ma)007:1875: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK016(ma)007:1876: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK016(ma)007:1877: zhes pas tshig gi ji ltar ston pa'i mchod pa rnams mkha' khyab tu sprul te dbul lo //
NK016(ma)007:1879: bdag dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi thugs ka nas ram dpag tu med pa chad /
NK016(ma)007:1881: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bas sems can
NK016(ma)007:1882: thams cad kyi snying nang na gnas pa'i rigs drug
NK016(ma)007:1883: gi sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa bsregs /
NK016(ma)007:1884: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su spar bar bsam zhing /
NK016(ma)007:1886: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK016(ma)007:1887: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK016(ma)007:1888: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK016(ma)007:1889: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK016(ma)007:1890: bcu gcig pa sbyor mchod ni /
NK016(ma)007:1891: rang dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha yab yum thams cad kyi mkha' gsang /
NK016(ma)007:1895: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK016(ma)007:1896: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK016(ma)007:1900: rjes su chags pa'i sbyor bas snyoms par zhugs te /
NK016(ma)007:1901: byang chub kyi sems sprin spro bsdu'i sbyor bas bde
NK016(ma)007:1902: ba chen po'i ye shes mchog tu rgyas pa la
NK016(ma)007:1904: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)007:1905: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK016(ma)007:1906: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK016(ma)007:1907: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK016(ma)007:1908: sa rba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu
NK016(ma)007:1909: r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK016(ma)007:1911: bcu gnyis pa 'dod yon ro mnyam gyi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1913: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK016(ma)007:1914: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK016(ma)007:1916: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol //
NK016(ma)007:1917: 'dod yon gyi snang ba thams cad lha dang lha mor dag pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:1918: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad bde ba chen po ro gcig tu gyur par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:1919: bcu gsum pa rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:1921: bla med mchog gi mchod pa sbyar ba 'di //
NK016(ma)007:1922: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK016(ma)007:1923: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK016(ma)007:1924: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:1925: zhes pas mchod pa'i rol mo ji snyed pa thams
NK016(ma)007:1926: cad kyi 'khor gsum ye shes su dag pa mngon
NK016(ma)007:1927: du byas nas / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma
NK016(ma)007:1928: h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK016(ma)007:1929: du byas nas / / zhes nga rgyas bya zhing rol mo ye shes kyi sgras bskul lo //
NK016(ma)007:1930: bcu bzhi pa glu ye shes kyi mchod pa ni //
NK016(ma)007:1931: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK016(ma)007:1932: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK016(ma)007:1933: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:1934: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs //
NK016(ma)007:1936: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK016(ma)007:1937: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK016(ma)007:1938: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK016(ma)007:1939: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che //
NK016(ma)007:1941: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK016(ma)007:1942: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK016(ma)007:1943: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK016(ma)007:1944: 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che //
NK016(ma)007:1946: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK016(ma)007:1947: mtha' yas kun nas sna tshogs spro //
NK016(ma)007:1948: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK016(ma)007:1949: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po //
NK016(ma)007:1951: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK016(ma)007:1952: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK016(ma)007:1953: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK016(ma)007:1954: skan cig yud la lhun gyis grub //
NK016(ma)007:1956: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)007:1957: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK016(ma)007:1958: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK016(ma)007:1959: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che //
NK016(ma)007:1960: hoh zhes pas zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)007:1962: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK016(ma)007:1964: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK016(ma)007:1965: mche ba zangs yag za byed che //
NK016(ma)007:1967: rngams pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK016(ma)007:1968: gtum chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK016(ma)007:1969: a la ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK016(ma)007:1970: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yengs pa che //
NK016(ma)007:1972: khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK016(ma)007:1973: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK016(ma)007:1975: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che //
NK016(ma)007:1977: khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK016(ma)007:1980: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che //
NK016(ma)007:1982: bdud kun gyi ni bdag chen po //
NK016(ma)007:1983: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms //
NK016(ma)007:1985: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che //
NK016(ma)007:1987: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK016(ma)007:1988: rdo rje chu ste sdud chen po //
NK016(ma)007:1989: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK016(ma)007:1990: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che //
NK016(ma)007:1991: hoh zhes pas khro bo ste /
NK016(ma)007:1992: chos nyid kyi rang sgra bstod dbyangs rgya mtsho'i rol mor kun tu sgrog par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:1993: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:1995: hoh spros pa med pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa na /
NK016(ma)007:1996: dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom
NK016(ma)007:1997: ldan 'das rnam thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)007:1998: bye brag dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo
NK016(ma)007:1999: rje sems dpa' la sogs pa rigs lnga'i bde bar
NK016(ma)007:2000: gshegs pa rigs mchog gzungs kyi yum gyi dbyings na
NK016(ma)007:2001: rnam par bzhugs pa sems dpa'i tshogs sems ma'i 'khor
NK016(ma)007:2002: / ye shes chen po'i dbang phyug thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)007:2005: ngo bo nyid kyi sku ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad dgongs su gsol /
NK016(ma)007:2006: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK016(ma)007:2007: dang po gsang ba rdo rje theg pa'i sgor khas 'ches te /
NK016(ma)007:2008: dam tshig gnyan po ma nor bar mnos pa las /
NK016(ma)007:2009: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag dang 'gal 'khrul du gyur pa /
NK016(ma)007:2010: lha nye bar ma bsgoms pa /
NK016(ma)007:2011: snying po dag par ma bgrangs pa /
NK016(ma)007:2012: sbyor ba mang po'i bar bskums pa /
NK016(ma)007:2013: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK016(ma)007:2014: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK016(ma)007:2015: mchod pa lo zla las 'das pa /
NK016(ma)007:2016: dam rdzas lag len rngo ma thogs pa /
NK016(ma)007:2019: ting nge 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa /
NK016(ma)007:2020: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod dam pa klong du ma gyur cing /
NK016(ma)007:2021: sems can gyi spyod pa rang thad du gyur pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2022: khyad par du sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK016(ma)007:2023: khyad par gyi dam tshig gnyan po mngon par mnos pa las /
NK016(ma)007:2024: nyams shing zhig ral du gyur pa ci mchis pa
NK016(ma)007:2025: thams cad shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis
NK016(ma)007:2026: mthol zhing bshags par mchis na /
NK016(ma)007:2027: dbyings nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i ngang gi sku bzod pa chen po dang du bzhes nas /
NK016(ma)007:2028: tshangs pa mchog yid bzhin du thob par stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2029: bzhi pa dngos grub gsol ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2030: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK016(ma)007:2036: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs kyi bla
NK016(ma)007:2037: man chad nas dngos grub kyi skal ba dang rigs
NK016(ma)007:2038: brgyud gang lags pa thams cad phyi mar bsdad mi
NK016(ma)007:2039: 'tshal bar dus da lta nyid du thob par stsal
NK016(ma)007:2040: du gsol / rnal 'byor pa la bar du gcod par byed pa /
NK016(ma)007:2048: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa dang ltas ngan pa
NK016(ma)007:2049: dang mi shes pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad phyir
NK016(ma)007:2050: bzlog cing ming tsam yang mi grags par zhi ba
NK016(ma)007:2052: gal te zhi bas bsgyur du mi btub pa zhig mchis na yang /
NK016(ma)007:2053: drag po'i phrin las kyis dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK016(ma)007:2055: bsgral zhing spar ba la sogs te /
NK016(ma)007:2056: phrin las drag thabs rnam bzhis ji ltar 'dul ba
NK016(ma)007:2057: 'tshams pa bzhin mdzad nas ming tsam yang mi grags
NK016(ma)007:2059: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du zhugs pa rnams //
NK016(ma)007:2060: bcad gtubs sdug bsngal lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur yang //
NK016(ma)007:2061: grib ma phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pas //
NK016(ma)007:2062: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong bas mod la 'tsho ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:2063: gzi mdangs lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag gi //
NK016(ma)007:2064: 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'byung ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:2065: lus ngag sems la tshe 'dir rdo rje rab snang ste //
NK016(ma)007:2066: re smon thams cad dus 'di nyid du stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2068: lnga pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2070: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK016(ma)007:2071: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:2072: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK016(ma)007:2073: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK016(ma)007:2074: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK016(ma)007:2075: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK016(ma)007:2076: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK016(ma)007:2077: rdo rje rgyal pos byin rlobs mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:2079: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrub //
NK016(ma)007:2080: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK016(ma)007:2082: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:2084: dang po nyams chag sbyang zhing dngos grub blang ba'i 'dzab la'ang /
NK016(ma)007:2087: skabs kyi 'jug bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK016(ma)007:2088: dang po ni dbye bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gsal btab nas /
NK016(ma)007:2089: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he phata dzah h+aum s+w+aa +aam
NK016(ma)007:2090: h+aa phata dzah h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram phata
NK016(ma)007:2092: dam tshig gi 'khor lo las ye shes kyi dkyil
NK016(ma)007:2093: 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa logs su phye
NK016(ma)007:2094: nas mdun gyi nam mkhar me ri 'dabs 'byar gyi
NK016(ma)007:2095: tshul du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:2097: bdag mdun gyi dam pa rigs brgya khyab byed kyi
NK016(ma)007:2098: rigs gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum dang
NK016(ma)007:2099: bcas pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa' so
NK016(ma)007:2100: so'i thugs kar yi ge brgya pa'i yi ge re
NK016(ma)007:2101: re zhing rang rang gi ting 'dzin sems dpa'i ngo
NK016(ma)007:2102: bor gsal bar ba sam la /
NK016(ma)007:2104: bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer mchod
NK016(ma)007:2105: pa'i tshul du spros pas ye shes kyi lha tshogs
NK016(ma)007:2109: yi ge so so las byung ba'i 'od zer nam mkha' gang bar 'phros /
NK016(ma)007:2110: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa thams cad kyi thugs dam bskul /
NK016(ma)007:2112: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams cad 'od dang 'od zer gyi rnam par bsdus /
NK016(ma)007:2113: mdun bskyed kyi lha rnams la thim /
NK016(ma)007:2114: gzi byin mchog tu 'bar ba'i 'od zer phyogs bcur
NK016(ma)007:2115: 'phros pa bdag dang sems can thams cad la phog
NK016(ma)007:2116: pas rtog sgrib nyams chag thams cad dag /
NK016(ma)007:2118: rang snang ye shes kyi 'khor lor gnyis med du gyur par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2119: dam ye 'phro 'du ste gsal ba gsum dang ldan pa'i ngang nas skyon bcu spangs te /
NK016(ma)007:2122: badz+ra sa t+aa t+we no pa tish+tha /
NK016(ma)007:2126: a nu rak+to me b+ha wa /
NK016(ma)007:2130: ha ha ha ha hoh b+ha ga w+aan sarba ta
NK016(ma)007:2131: th+aa ga ta badz+ra m+aa me muny+tsa badz+ri b+ha wa
NK016(ma)007:2132: ma h+aa sa ma ya sat+aa +aahh+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:2133: ces brgya stong sogs ci nus bazla'o //
NK016(ma)007:2134: yang na 'dzab khang ma phye bar /
NK016(ma)007:2135: sngar rang nyid gtso bo gnyis pa'i rnam par thon
NK016(ma)007:2136: pa'i las kyi rdo rje sems dpa' de nyid sems
NK016(ma)007:2137: dpa' sum brtsegs kyi rnam par bsgoms pa'i ting 'dzin
NK016(ma)007:2138: sems dpa' h+aum gi mthar yig brgya'i sngags phreng bkod
NK016(ma)007:2139: pa las 'phros pa'i 'od kyis tshogs rten mdun bskyed
NK016(ma)007:2140: kyi lha tshogs rnams bskul ba sogs kyi phyag len
NK016(ma)007:2141: kyang snang ste don gyi gnad gcig go //
NK016(ma)007:2142: ting nge 'dzin la blo goms pa dag gis ni /
NK016(ma)007:2143: 'dzab khang dabye'am ma dbye yang rung ste /
NK016(ma)007:2144: lus kyi sgul bskyod thams cad lha'i phyag rgya /
NK016(ma)007:2145: ngag rlung 'byung 'jug thams cad sngags kyi sgra gdangs /
NK016(ma)007:2146: sems dran rtog thams cad chos nyid byang chub sems kyi ngo bor rtogs pas zla'o //
NK016(ma)007:2147: gsum pa skabs kyi 'jug bsdu ba la /
NK016(ma)007:2150: 'dzab khang bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK016(ma)007:2153: yang na zhi khro'i gzhi bstod gnyis sbrel nas byas kyang rung zhing /
NK016(ma)007:2155: mi rtog rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK016(ma)007:2156: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK016(ma)007:2157: thugs rje'i bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK016(ma)007:2158: rdo rje sems dpa' che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK016(ma)007:2159: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK016(ma)007:2160: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga'i gtso //
NK016(ma)007:2161: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya chen rol pa'i lha //
NK016(ma)007:2162: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK016(ma)007:2165: ye nas gnyis med chos skur dag pa las //
NK016(ma)007:2166: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK016(ma)007:2167: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK016(ma)007:2168: de ldog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos te //
NK016(ma)007:2169: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK016(ma)007:2170: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur pas //
NK016(ma)007:2171: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK016(ma)007:2172: thugs rje che mnga' khyod la bzod par gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2173: zhes bzlas pa'i nyes byas su gyur pa rnams bshags /
NK016(ma)007:2175: dam ye'i dkyil 'khor rang bzhin dbyer med du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK016(ma)007:2177: zhes sogs kyis zhi khro'i rig pa'i me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul ba /
NK016(ma)007:2178: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya hoh zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK016(ma)007:2179: dzahh+aum bam hohs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dam tshig
NK016(ma)007:2180: gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis med du bstim nas gsal
NK016(ma)007:2181: brtan dbang du byas te yi ge brgya pa'ang bazla'o
NK016(ma)007:2183: slar yang rang nyid gtso bo gnyis pa'i rnam par phye la bum par gzungs thag gtad de /
NK016(ma)007:2184: bdag gi snying ga nas sngags kyi phreng ba gzungs thag la 'khril te song /
NK016(ma)007:2185: bum pa'i lha rigs lnga yab yum so so'i ye
NK016(ma)007:2186: shes sems dpa'i thugs ka'i ting nge 'dzin sems dpa'
NK016(ma)007:2187: h+aum m+aum sogs sa bon so so'i mthar g.yas bskor
NK016(ma)007:2188: du rigs so so'i kha dog can du 'khod /
NK016(ma)007:2189: lha rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)007:2190: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs dam bskul /
NK016(ma)007:2191: byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams cad bsdus /
NK016(ma)007:2192: bum pa'i lha la thim pas sku'i cha thams cad
NK016(ma)007:2193: dang sbyor mtshams nas byang sems ye shes kyi bdud
NK016(ma)007:2194: rtsir babs pas bum pa ga nga bar bsam zhing
NK016(ma)007:2195: rigs lnga so so la dmigs pa'i yig brgya mang
NK016(ma)007:2197: rigs lnga so so'i sngags sam spyi sngags bod+d+hi tsit+ta yang bazla'o //
NK016(ma)007:2198: slar yang khro bo rigs lnga'i bskyed sngags rnams brjod pas /
NK016(ma)007:2199: zhi ba rigs lnga khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum
NK016(ma)007:2200: gyi skur gyur pa so so'i thugs kar h+aum yig
NK016(ma)007:2201: he ru ka'i yig brgyas bskor bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2202: badz+ra he ru ka sa ma ya /
NK016(ma)007:2204: badz+ra he ru ka t+we no zhes pa nas /
NK016(ma)007:2205: he ru ka m+aa me muny+tsa he ru ko b+ha wa ma h+aa sa ma ya sat+wa +aahh+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:2207: khrag 'thung yab yum so so'i sngags sam /
NK016(ma)007:2209: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK016(ma)007:2211: gtso sngags kyi mthar chu phul bas /
NK016(ma)007:2212: lha thams cad chags pa chen pos ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)007:2213: bdud rtsir zhu ba bum chu dang ro gcig tu
NK016(ma)007:2215: gsum pa las sbyor gyi bzlas pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2216: tshogs rten la brten nas tshogs bsags pa gtso bor
NK016(ma)007:2217: byed pa'i skabs 'dir las sbyor gyi bzlas pa ma
NK016(ma)007:2218: byas na'ang chad pa'i skyon med la /
NK016(ma)007:2219: 'on kyang dmigs yul la phan gdags pa sogs kyi
NK016(ma)007:2220: dgos pa khyad par can gyi slad du bzlas par
NK016(ma)007:2221: spro na / dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyi zhal nas sngags kyi sgra dang /
NK016(ma)007:2222: thugs rje'i 'od zer 'phros pas khams gsum thams cad snang bar byas /
NK016(ma)007:2224: dmigs yul gtso bor gyur pa'i sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing du bsgral bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2226: da ha da ha sogs ngan song sbyong ba'i las sngags btags pa brgya rtsa sogs bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK016(ma)007:2227: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi yang
NK016(ma)007:2228: snying yi ge brgya pa zhes bya ba nyams chag
NK016(ma)007:2229: dang rtog sgrib thams cad sbyong bar byed pa 'di
NK016(ma)007:2230: bzlas pas / rnal 'byor pa rtog sgrib can /
NK016(ma)007:2232: gsog 'jog can bag chags ngan pa can khyed rnams kyi nyams chag thams cad skongs te /
NK016(ma)007:2233: ngan song du ltung pa'i las kyi sgrib pa las thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2234: tshe 'di la yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras
NK016(ma)007:2235: kyi dam par dgongs nas bsrung zhing skyob par mdzad
NK016(ma)007:2236: la / shi 'phos nas kyang bde bar gshegs pa
NK016(ma)007:2237: rnams kyi sras kyi thu bor 'gyur bar gdon mi
NK016(ma)007:2238: la / za'o // zhes gnang ba byin par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:2239: bdun pa bskang ba bya ba bdun las /
NK016(ma)007:2241: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku
NK016(ma)007:2242: chen po'i klong du 'khor 'das ro mnyam par bltas
NK016(ma)007:2244: bskang ngo kalpasa thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2245: dngos po stong nyid klong du bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2246: snang ba ye shes klong du gsal ba shes rab
NK016(ma)007:2247: sdug bsngal chos nyid skye ba med pa'i dbyings su
NK016(ma)007:2248: 'gag pa med pa'i mkha' la skye 'gag gnyis med
NK016(ma)007:2249: klong du nyams chag skongs shing rtog sgrib dag /
NK016(ma)007:2250: dbang dang dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2251: gnyis pa bdud rtsis bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2253: bskang ngo bdud rtsis thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2254: kun gzhi klong yangs b+hany+dza ru //
NK016(ma)007:2255: byang chub sems kyi bdud rtsis bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2256: 'di yang rang byung bdud rtsi ste //
NK016(ma)007:2257: dmigs med chos sku'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2259: ye shes sgrib med bdud rtsis bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2260: 'di yang rang byung bdud rtsi ste //
NK016(ma)007:2261: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2263: thig le 'bar ba'i bdud rtsis bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2264: 'di yang rang byung rgyal ba sprul sku'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2265: ye shes rtsa lnga'i b+hany+dza ru //
NK016(ma)007:2266: skye med a dkar bdud rtsis bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2267: 'di yang rang byung zhi ba'i lha tshogs thugs dam /
NK016(ma)007:2269: shes rab rang gsal bdud rtsis bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2270: 'di yang rang byung khro bo'i lha tshogs thugs dam bdud rtsi sman gyi dam tshig 'dis //
NK016(ma)007:2271: mchod 'os rgya mtsho'i thugs dam nyams chag skongs shing rtog sgrib dag /
NK016(ma)007:2272: dbang dang dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2273: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:2274: zhes brjod la rol mo bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:2275: gsum pa gtor mas bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2277: bskang ngo gtor mas thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2279: shangs kyi rlung sgrom dpal bshos btsugs //
NK016(ma)007:2281: sgron ma mig gi dza gad stsal //
NK016(ma)007:2282: dbang po lnga yi rak+tasa brgyan //
NK016(ma)007:2283: 'di yang rang byung gtor ma ste //
NK016(ma)007:2284: bla ma rig 'dzin mchog gsum dang //
NK016(ma)007:2285: zhi khro rab 'byams thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2286: nyi zla kha sbyor gtor gzhong du //
NK016(ma)007:2289: rnam shes tshogs brgyad dza gad stsal //
NK016(ma)007:2290: rtsa chen bzhi yi rak+tasa brgyan //
NK016(ma)007:2291: 'di yang rang byung gtor ma ste //
NK016(ma)007:2292: bla ma rig 'dzin mchog gsum dang //
NK016(ma)007:2293: zhi khro rab 'byams thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2294: khyab brdal pags pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK016(ma)007:2295: rus pa rang snang dpal bshos btsugs //
NK016(ma)007:2296: rang snang sha yi mtheb kyus bskor //
NK016(ma)007:2297: bkrag dang mdangs kyi dza gad stsal //
NK016(ma)007:2298: khrag dang chu ser rak+tasa brgyan //
NK016(ma)007:2299: 'di yang rang byung gtor ma ste //
NK016(ma)007:2300: bla ma rig 'dzin mchog gsum dang //
NK016(ma)007:2301: zhi khro rab 'byams thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2302: khog pa stong pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK016(ma)007:2303: mchin pa rang snang dpal bshos btsugs //
NK016(ma)007:2304: glo mtsher mkhal ma'i mtheb kyus bskor //
NK016(ma)007:2305: gu h+ya nang khrol dza gad stsal //
NK016(ma)007:2306: rang snang mkhris pa'i rak+tasa brgyan //
NK016(ma)007:2307: 'di yang rang byung bla ma rig 'dzin zhi khro rab 'byams ba lim 'dod yon dam tshig 'dis //
NK016(ma)007:2308: mchod 'os rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2309: nyams chag skongs shing dbang dang dngos grub ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:2311: bzhi pa rak+tasa bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2313: bskang ngo rak+tasa thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2314: spyi bo bde chen b+hany+dza ru //
NK016(ma)007:2315: sdug bsngal rnam rtog rak+tasa bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2317: bla ma rig 'dzin zhi khro mgrin pa longs spyod b+hany+tsa ru //
NK016(ma)007:2318: sna tshogs yid kyi rak+tasa 'di yang bla ma zhi
NK016(ma)007:2319: khro snying ga chos kyi bsam pa blo yi 'di
NK016(ma)007:2320: yang bla ma zhi khro lte ba sprul pa'i nyon
NK016(ma)007:2321: mongs srid rtsa'i 'di yang bla ma zhi khro gsang
NK016(ma)007:2322: ba bde skyong bde ba thig le'i 'di yang bla
NK016(ma)007:2323: ma zhi khro rak+ta 'bar ba'i dam tshig 'dis //
NK016(ma)007:2324: mchod 'os rgya mtsho'i nyams chag skongs shing /
NK016(ma)007:2328: lnga pa sgron mes bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2330: bskang ngo sgron mes thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2331: brdal khyab pags pa'i kong bu ru //
NK016(ma)007:2332: khrag dang chu ser mar khus gtams //
NK016(ma)007:2333: sha dang rus pa'i sdong bu la //
NK016(ma)007:2334: rang gsal bkra mdangs zhun mar spar //
NK016(ma)007:2335: 'di yang rang byung sgron me ste //
NK016(ma)007:2336: bla ma zhi khro dung chen 'bar ba'i kong go
NK016(ma)007:2337: ro tsa na'i mar gsal byed rtsa lnga'i sdong dbang
NK016(ma)007:2338: po sgo lnga'i zhun 'di yang rang byung sgron bla
NK016(ma)007:2339: ma zhi khro tsit+ta 'bar ba'i snying tshil dkar dmar
NK016(ma)007:2340: pad+ma 'dab brgyad rnam shes tshogs brgyad zhun 'di yang
NK016(ma)007:2341: bla ma zhi khro a wa d+h+au ti'i rang gsal
NK016(ma)007:2342: 'od kyi 'khor lo bdun brtsegs byang chub sems kyi
NK016(ma)007:2343: 'di yang bla ma zhi khro mi shigs thig le'i
NK016(ma)007:2344: skye med ye shes rtsa phran bcu gnyis rig pa
NK016(ma)007:2345: rang byung 'di yang bla ma zhi khro ye shes
NK016(ma)007:2346: rtsa lnga'i a dkar rtsa gcig ye shes 'od zer
NK016(ma)007:2347: shes rab 'bru lnga'i 'di yang bla ma zhi khro
NK016(ma)007:2348: mchog gi 'od gsal gangs gsal 'od kyi thig le
NK016(ma)007:2349: 'bar ba'i ye shes lnga yi 'di yang bla ma
NK016(ma)007:2350: zhi khro kun gzhi klong yangs chos kyi dbyings kyi
NK016(ma)007:2351: byang chub sems kyi sku lnga lhun grub 'di yang
NK016(ma)007:2353: bla ma rig 'dzin zhi khro rab 'byams sgron ma 'bar ba'i dam tshig 'dis //
NK016(ma)007:2354: mchod 'os rgya mtsho'i nyams chag skongs shing dbang dang dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2355: d+ai pa pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:2362: chag nyams dang rtog sgrib thams cad sh+ain+tam ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:2363: zhes khrus bdun gyi rig pa lan bdun du bazla'o //
NK016(ma)007:2364: drug pa zhi ba gnas dag gis bskang ba ni //
NK016(ma)007:2365: phung po lnga po gnas dag pa //
NK016(ma)007:2366: rgyal ba yab lnga'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2367: 'byung ba lnga po gnas dag pa //
NK016(ma)007:2368: rgyal ba yum lnga'i yid chos gnyis po kun bzang
NK016(ma)007:2369: yab yum rnam shes tshogs brgyad sems dpa' brgyad kyi
NK016(ma)007:2370: thugs dam rnam shes yul brgyad gnas dag pa //
NK016(ma)007:2371: sems ma brgyad kyi lus kyi chos bzhi gnas khro
NK016(ma)007:2372: bo bzhi yi rtag chad mu bzhi gnas khro mo
NK016(ma)007:2373: bzhi yi nyon mongs drug po gnas thub pa drug
NK016(ma)007:2374: gi bdun pa khro bo gnas gyur gyis bskang ba
NK016(ma)007:2376: nyon mongs dug lnga gnas gyur pa //
NK016(ma)007:2377: khrag 'thung yab lnga'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2378: 'byung ba lus lnga gnas gyur pa //
NK016(ma)007:2379: khrag 'thung yum lnga'i rnam 'gyur tshogs brgyad gnas khro
NK016(ma)007:2380: mo brgyad kyi rnam 'gyur yul brgyad phra men brgyad
NK016(ma)007:2381: kyi rtag chad mtha' bzhi gnas sgo ma bzhi yi
NK016(ma)007:2382: sna tshogs rtog pa dbang mo nyer brgyad mi shigs
NK016(ma)007:2384: 'gag med gsung gi thugs 'gyur med thugs kyi thugs
NK016(ma)007:2385: yon tan mi zad thugs phrin las rgyan gyi thugs
NK016(ma)007:2386: ye shes 'khor lo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)007:2387: nyams chag thams cad skongs gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:2388: rtog sgrib thams cad dag gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:2389: bskangs gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)007:2390: zhes pas phyi nang gsang ba'i 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK016(ma)007:2391: thams cad 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)007:2392: dbyings su ro mnyam par bskang pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:2393: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la lnga ste /
NK016(ma)007:2398: bsngo ba bya zhing shis pa brjod pa'o //
NK016(ma)007:2399: dang po tshogs mchod la yang lnga las /
NK016(ma)007:2400: dang po bsham zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2401: dam rdzas su 'os pa'i yo byad rnams bshams nas /
NK016(ma)007:2403: ram yam kham gis dngos 'dzin nyes skyon bsregs gtor bkrus te dag par byas /
NK016(ma)007:2405: zhal zas kyi snod du nyi ma la h+aum s+w+aa
NK016(ma)007:2406: +aam h+aa las bza' btung gi dngos po ye shes
NK016(ma)007:2407: lnga'i rang bzhin bdud rtsi ro brgya pa 'dod yon
NK016(ma)007:2408: gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa so so'i
NK016(ma)007:2409: lha mo'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK016(ma)007:2410: bcas pa'i sprin 'phro bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2411: yi ge gsum lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlab /
NK016(ma)007:2412: gnyis pa tshogs zhing spyan drang ba ni //
NK016(ma)007:2413: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK016(ma)007:2414: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK016(ma)007:2416: tshogs mchog dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2418: ru lu ru lu e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes pas spyan drangs la /
NK016(ma)007:2419: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga am ku sha dzah p+aa sha h+aum /
NK016(ma)007:2421: g+han+de hoh zhes dgug gzhug bcing mnyes bya /
NK016(ma)007:2422: gsum pa mchod pa la gnyis kyi /
NK016(ma)007:2423: dang po spyir mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2424: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au sogs bzhi bsnol dang /
NK016(ma)007:2426: rdo rje sgeg mo rdo rje can //
NK016(ma)007:2427: sems dpa' sngon mo'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK016(ma)007:2428: me long lta bu'i ye shes las //
NK016(ma)007:2429: badz+ra l+aa s+ya'i mchod pa rol sh+r+ai r+aa ga l+aa s+ya h+aum /
NK016(ma)007:2432: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las //
NK016(ma)007:2433: badz+ra m+aa le'i mchod m+aa le t+r+aam /
NK016(ma)007:2434: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK016(ma)007:2435: spyan ras gzigs kyi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK016(ma)007:2436: so sor rtog pa'i ye badz+ra g+ai ti'i mchod g+ai ti h+r+aih gar mkhan 'gying bag gzi ldan ma //
NK016(ma)007:2438: bya ba nan tan ye shes las //
NK016(ma)007:2439: badz+ra n+ri ti'i mchod par rol //
NK016(ma)007:2441: gnyis pa khyad par gyi mchod pa la gsum las /
NK016(ma)007:2442: tshogs phud cha gsum mam bzhir spros la /
NK016(ma)007:2445: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK016(ma)007:2446: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK016(ma)007:2447: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK016(ma)007:2448: thugs dam bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2449: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos //
NK016(ma)007:2450: 'dod yon lha mos nam mkha' gang //
NK016(ma)007:2452: spyan sogs bde bas tshim gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:2453: +aahh+aum su ta ra ta u pa b+h+yahk+aa ma h+aa
NK016(ma)007:2454: h+ai pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh zhes 'dod yon lnga'i mchod
NK016(ma)007:2458: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK016(ma)007:2459: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa'i dam tshig la //
NK016(ma)007:2460: sems can dbang gis nor 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK016(ma)007:2461: mi 'chab 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK016(ma)007:2462: yi ge brgya pa'ang brjod cing 'khon gcugs dag par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:2464: lid+ga logs su ma bcas na tshogs phud tha ma
NK016(ma)007:2465: de'i 'dod yon gyi lha mo h+aum zhes rang la
NK016(ma)007:2466: bsdus pa'am / sngar byin rlabs kyi gong du bcad na ni der zad la /
NK016(ma)007:2467: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:2468: bdag nyid rdo rje khro bo'i skur gyur //
NK016(ma)007:2470: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)007:2471: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2472: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2473: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2474: zhi khro sgyu 'phrul rnam par rol ba'i lha tshogs rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2475: sprul pa yang sprul phyag brnyan dang bcas pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2476: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis ma rungs
NK016(ma)007:2477: pa'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa thams
NK016(ma)007:2478: cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par
NK016(ma)007:2479: gyur cig / n+ri yam dzahn+ri badz+ra am ku sha
NK016(ma)007:2480: dzah tri yam dzahtri badz+ra am ku sha dzah zhes
NK016(ma)007:2481: lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas bkug la /
NK016(ma)007:2482: dzahh+aum bam hohs dgug bcings bsdams nas myos par byas
NK016(ma)007:2483: te 'dug pa'i snying gar dwangs ma ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)007:2484: a dkar po dang bcas pa /
NK016(ma)007:2485: bdag dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK016(ma)007:2487: gzas po'i snying ga'i sgo phye /
NK016(ma)007:2490: dug lnga ye shes su gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)007:2491: dwangs ma sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'khor lor spar te sangs rgyas par gyur /
NK016(ma)007:2492: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka m+aa ra badz+ra sarba dush+tana /
NK016(ma)007:2494: ma tam kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:2495: hri da ya bi pa h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:2496: snyigs ma rang snang sgyu 'phrul gyi 'khor lo khro
NK016(ma)007:2497: tshogs 'bar bas rdo rje bza' ba'i dam tshig tu
NK016(ma)007:2500: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK016(ma)007:2501: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:2502: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK016(ma)007:2503: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK016(ma)007:2505: sarba dush+tana m+aa ra ya h+aum phata kyis lid+ga'i gnas
NK016(ma)007:2506: lngar phur bu btab pas bsad cing bcad gtubs khog
NK016(ma)007:2508: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK016(ma)007:2512: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha kha le le le h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)007:2515: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:2516: rgod dang gshe dang 'jig par ston pa dang //
NK016(ma)007:2517: snying rje rngams dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK016(ma)007:2518: sku yi dngos po shin tu sgyur pa yin //
NK016(ma)007:2519: gar yang sgrub po rnal 'byor las //
NK016(ma)007:2520: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK016(ma)007:2521: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK016(ma)007:2522: m+aam sa la sogs ro mchog gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2523: me tog la sogs tsan+dana dri //
NK016(ma)007:2524: bzang rgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2525: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK016(ma)007:2526: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK016(ma)007:2527: sgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK016(ma)007:2528: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:2529: ces pas bsgral mtha' sbyor ba'i dam tshig chen por
NK016(ma)007:2530: bsgrubs pas lha thams cad cad tshim par byas la
NK016(ma)007:2532: ces pas zhi bar nga rgyal 'phos te /
NK016(ma)007:2535: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK016(ma)007:2536: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK016(ma)007:2537: bcom ldan bde gshegs thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK016(ma)007:2538: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK016(ma)007:2539: phyag brnyan khro gtum rngams pa'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK016(ma)007:2540: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK016(ma)007:2541: dgyes par rol cig mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK016(ma)007:2542: bzhes te a la la yis dgyes par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:2548: dzahh+aum bam hoh bra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes 'khor gsum bde ba chen por ro mnyam mo //
NK016(ma)007:2549: bzhi pa tshogs la rol pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2550: lnga pa lhag ma gtong ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2551: bla ma rnams kyi phyag len la dbang gi mthar mdzad la /
NK016(ma)007:2552: chos skyong spyi sgos dang 'jig rten pa'i gtor ma
NK016(ma)007:2553: bsngo ba rnams ni 'dir byas na skabs su bab
NK016(ma)007:2554: par 'gyur ro // gnyis pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2555: cho ga'i don 'gangs che shos gcig yin pa'i phyir dngos gzhi'i khongs su bsdebs nas /
NK016(ma)007:2556: tshogs mchod man chad rjes kyi rtsis 'gos bsdus nang legs mod kyi /
NK016(ma)007:2558: de ltar gong ma'i phyag len bzhin 'dir bya ste /
NK016(ma)007:2559: de la bdag nyid 'jug pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2560: gzhan la dbang bskur gnyis kyi /
NK016(ma)007:2562: rtsa ba'i bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo
NK016(ma)007:2563: tha mi dad pa dbang len pa'i yul du byas
NK016(ma)007:2564: nas / dbang gi bya ba rnams gtso bo las
NK016(ma)007:2565: phye ba'i rgyal thebs kyis mdzad par mos te dbang
NK016(ma)007:2567: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang rang bzhin dbyer
NK016(ma)007:2568: med du bsgoms nas rig pa 'i me tog dor
NK016(ma)007:2569: ba nyid don gyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'ang yin
NK016(ma)007:2570: pas / gzhan la dbang bskur dang 'brel na phyi ma dang /
NK016(ma)007:2571: ma 'brel na snga ma ltar byas pas gnas skabs su spros pa 'tshams par 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2573: de gnyis gang gi mthar yang dkyil 'khor la thal mo sbyor bas btud de //
NK016(ma)007:2574: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:2575: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)007:2578: zhes gsol bas gnang ba byin par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:2579: gnyis pa slob mar dbang bskur ba la gsum gyi /
NK016(ma)007:2580: dang po 'jug pa la dgu las /
NK016(ma)007:2581: dang po khrus sogs bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2582: dkyil 'khor khang pa'i phyi rol du khrus byas /
NK016(ma)007:2586: +aa kham w+ai ra h+aum gis me tog gtad /
NK016(ma)007:2587: gnyis pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2588: kye ma kyi hud rdo rje 'dzin //
NK016(ma)007:2589: 'gro mgon thugs rjes bdag skyobs shig /
NK016(ma)007:2590: dbang mchog rgyal po bsgrag tu gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2591: slad nas mi 'chab mi sbed do //
NK016(ma)007:2593: gsum pa gnang ba byin pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2594: bu 'dir shog cig rigs kyi bu //
NK016(ma)007:2595: rang gi nyams dang zlas nyams kyis //
NK016(ma)007:2596: na rags gnas su ltung ba las //
NK016(ma)007:2597: skyob phyir dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK016(ma)007:2598: zhes brjod la yol ba'i nang du drang /
NK016(ma)007:2600: nyes byas bshags sdom gyi bsam pa drag pos /
NK016(ma)007:2601: kye ma kyi hud bdag 'dra bas //
NK016(ma)007:2602: las ngan rnam smin myong 'gyur na //
NK016(ma)007:2603: nyes byas 'gyod pas mthol lo bshags //
NK016(ma)007:2604: mgon po'i thugs rjes bdag sgrol cig /
NK016(ma)007:2605: lnga pa sems bskyed pa la gnyis las /
NK016(ma)007:2607: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)007:2610: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK016(ma)007:2612: drug pa me tog dor ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2613: sngar gtad pa'i me tog thal mos bzung ste /
NK016(ma)007:2615: slob dpon sku yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK016(ma)007:2616: rin chen me tog 'di dor bas //
NK016(ma)007:2617: rnam par dag pa'i las gang gis //
NK016(ma)007:2618: thugs rjes mnyes par bgyid mdzad lha //
NK016(ma)007:2619: gang yin de la 'bab par shog /
NK016(ma)007:2621: pra ti sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)007:2622: bo d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)007:2623: zhes slob dpon gyi sku la 'dor du bcug nas
NK016(ma)007:2624: dbu la sogs pa sku'i gnas so so dang nye
NK016(ma)007:2625: ring las mtshon te mchog dang rab 'bring tha ma'i
NK016(ma)007:2626: dngos grub las 'di 'grub par 'gyur zhis brda sprad
NK016(ma)007:2627: / bdun pa me tog gi dbang ni /
NK016(ma)007:2629: dam tshig bden pa chen po'i mthu //
NK016(ma)007:2630: sngon sbyangs las kyis 'brel ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:2631: gnyis su med pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK016(ma)007:2632: mnyam par byin rlabs mdzad du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2633: h'u badz+ra sat+wa +aa be sha ya +aah zhes me tog gi phreng ba mgo bor bcing /
NK016(ma)007:2634: brgyad pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2636: ji ltar mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK016(ma)007:2637: ma rig ldongs pa bsal ba ltar //
NK016(ma)007:2638: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs kyi lhas //
NK016(ma)007:2639: skal ldan bu khyod mig dabye'o //
NK016(ma)007:2640: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)007:2641: ces pas mig dbye zhing gdong g.yogs dgrol /
NK016(ma)007:2642: dgu pa mthong ba stan pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2644: da ni dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK016(ma)007:2645: khyod ni sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK016(ma)007:2646: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs //
NK016(ma)007:2647: dngos grub thams cad phun sum tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:2648: dam tshig mchog tu khyod 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2650: bcom ldan 'das zhi khro rab 'byams kyi dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)007:2651: chen po rten dang brten par bcas pa thams cad
NK016(ma)007:2652: mngon sum bzhin du mthong bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)007:2653: gnyis pa dbang gi dngos gzhi la /
NK016(ma)007:2654: sbyor ba sdig sgrib dag byed dang /
NK016(ma)007:2655: dngos gzhi yon tan yar 'phel kyi dbang gnyis kyi dang po la bdun las /
NK016(ma)007:2657: slob ma khrus sa'i stan la bzhag ste /
NK016(ma)007:2658: thugs ka nas spros pa'i khro bo'i tshogs dang /
NK016(ma)007:2659: bi shwa badz+ra gyi sngags brjod pas bgegs rnams bskrad
NK016(ma)007:2660: par bsam la yungs thun gyis brab pa sogs bya'o
NK016(ma)007:2662: slob bus tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib thams cad gsang gnas su du /
NK016(ma)007:2664: snying gar pre rnams kyi rnam par gnas pa so
NK016(ma)007:2665: so'i steng du rig pa'i ye shes ram yam kham
NK016(ma)007:2666: gsum du gsal bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2667: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas 'phros pa'i 'od zer gyis 'byung ba'i yi ge gsum bskul /
NK016(ma)007:2668: ye shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas gsang gnas kyi du bsregs gtor sbyangs par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2670: yam s+pha kham s+pha ces spyangs /
NK016(ma)007:2672: slob dpon gyi lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga
NK016(ma)007:2673: la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du h+aum
NK016(ma)007:2674: s+w+aa +aam h+aa / yon gyi sor mo lnga la
NK016(ma)007:2675: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du m+aum l+aam
NK016(ma)007:2676: m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan pa rnams rigs lnga
NK016(ma)007:2677: yab yum bcur gyur par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2680: badz+ra any+tsa lis sor mo bsnol /
NK016(ma)007:2682: zhes bsdams pas rigs lnga yab yum mnyam par sbyor bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2683: bden pa'i stobs brjod cing thal mo dkrol nas /
NK016(ma)007:2684: na ra ka shud+d+ha tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)007:2685: ces brjod cing thal mo dkrugs pas /
NK016(ma)007:2686: slob dpon gyi thugs ka dang rigs lnga'i sbyor mtshams
NK016(ma)007:2687: nas 'od zer 'phros pas dmyal bar skye ba'i sa
NK016(ma)007:2688: bon bag chags dang bcas pa sbyangs par bsam mo
NK016(ma)007:2690: sngon las la 'gyod cing bshags sdom gyi bsam pas /
NK016(ma)007:2691: kye ma kyi hud rdo rje 'dzin //
NK016(ma)007:2692: zhes sogs kyis gsol ba gdab /
NK016(ma)007:2694: bu 'dir shog cig rang gi nyams na rag gnas su skyob phyir zhes dbang stegs su drang /
NK016(ma)007:2696: da ha da ha sarba na ra ka ga te he tum h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:2697: ces bzla zhing yungs kar gyis brab /
NK016(ma)007:2700: til gyi gong bu bzhin gang ba'i //
NK016(ma)007:2701: rgyal bas bum pa bzung nas ni //
NK016(ma)007:2702: 'di nyid du ni blugs mdzad pas //
NK016(ma)007:2703: bag chags ma lus dag gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:2706: da ha da ha sogs btags pa brjod bzhin du bkrus pas /
NK016(ma)007:2707: rigs kyi bu 'dis nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi
NK016(ma)007:2708: sgo nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib thams cad sh+aan+tinga ku
NK016(ma)007:2711: de bzhin du sa bcad gnyis pa man chad kyi
NK016(ma)007:2712: sgos chos bye brag pa rnams 'don pa spos nas
NK016(ma)007:2713: bya ste / slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od dang ram yam kham gis snying ga'i pre sbyangs /
NK016(ma)007:2715: pre ta tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)007:2716: yi dwags su skye ba'i sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa sbyangs /
NK016(ma)007:2717: kye ma kyi hud kyis gsol ba gdab /
NK016(ma)007:2718: bu 'dir sogs kyis rkang pa gsum pa /
NK016(ma)007:2719: pre ta'i gnas su zhes bsgyur bas drang /
NK016(ma)007:2720: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ka ga te he tum h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:2722: khrus bum gyis sngar bzhin bkru ba las /
NK016(ma)007:2724: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags kyi sgo nas bsags pa'i zhes sbyar /
NK016(ma)007:2726: thugs ka'i 'od dang ram yam kham gis lte ba'i tri sbyangs /
NK016(ma)007:2728: tir+ya ka ga te tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)007:2729: dud 'gror skye ba'i sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa sbyangs /
NK016(ma)007:2730: kye ma kyi hud kyis gsol ba gdab /
NK016(ma)007:2731: dud 'gro'i gnas su ltung ba las /
NK016(ma)007:2733: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ka ga te he tum h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)007:2735: khrus bum gyis sngar bzhin bkru ba las /
NK016(ma)007:2737: nyon mongs pa gti mug gi sgo nas bsags pa'i zhes sbyar ba dang /
NK016(ma)007:2738: skabs 'dir rnam snang dang mi 'khrugs pa'i gzungs sngags
NK016(ma)007:2739: bzla ba'ang bla ma rnams kyi phyag len gyi rgyun
NK016(ma)007:2740: la snang bas de lta yang bya zhing /
NK016(ma)007:2742: rigs kyi bus tshe 'khor ba thog ma med pa
NK016(ma)007:2743: nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib nyon mongs bag chags skal
NK016(ma)007:2744: ba ngan pa dang bkra mi shis pa'i dngos po
NK016(ma)007:2745: thams cad nye bar zhi ste shin tu bkra shis
NK016(ma)007:2746: par gyur cig / ces brjod do //
NK016(ma)007:2747: de dag ni ngan song gnas 'dren gyi dbang zhes bya ste /
NK016(ma)007:2748: bcud khyad par can bsgrub pa la sngon du snod dag par byed pa bzhin no //
NK016(ma)007:2749: gnyis pa yon tan yar 'phel gyi dbang bskur ba la bzhi las /
NK016(ma)007:2750: dang po rdo rje sems dpa'i bum pa'i dbang gis lus kyi dri ma sbyang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2751: slob ma seng ges btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri
NK016(ma)007:2752: sna tshogs pad+ma dang nyi zla brtsegs pa'i steng du
NK016(ma)007:2753: rdo rje sems dpa' yum dang bcas pa'i rnam pas
NK016(ma)007:2755: ye shes rgyal po sogs kyis gsol ba btab par gyur pa la /
NK016(ma)007:2756: slob dpon gyi rnam par rgyal ba'i bum pa spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK016(ma)007:2757: sku gsum dam tshig las byung ba //
NK016(ma)007:2758: nyon mongs zhe sdang 'joms pa yis //
NK016(ma)007:2759: lha yi bdud rtsi dag pa 'dis //
NK016(ma)007:2760: mi bskyod pa ru dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2761: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)007:2762: zhes bum chu spyi bor gtigs pas /
NK016(ma)007:2763: mi bskyod pa'i rang bzhin stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur /
NK016(ma)007:2765: bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK016(ma)007:2766: dbang gnas su bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma 'khyil ba las
NK016(ma)007:2767: mi bskyod pa sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu
NK016(ma)007:2769: de ltar na skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyi zhe sdang dag /
NK016(ma)007:2770: rnam par shes pa'i phung po mi bskyod par gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)007:2771: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK016(ma)007:2773: de bzhin du rna ltag g.yas su bum chu gtigs pa la /
NK016(ma)007:2774: sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal srid che //
NK016(ma)007:2775: ser sna'i rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)007:2776: rtag tu chags med sbyin pa 'dis //
NK016(ma)007:2777: rdzogs sangs rgyas su dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2778: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa rin 'byung gi rang bzhin
NK016(ma)007:2779: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes 'khyil ba las rin
NK016(ma)007:2781: tshor ba'i phung po rin chen 'byung ldan mnyam pa
NK016(ma)007:2782: nyid kyi yeshesa zhes sogs kyi khyad par ma gtogs
NK016(ma)007:2783: sngar ltar shes par byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:2784: ltag par bum chu sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK016(ma)007:2785: mi phyed rdo rje gsang ba las //
NK016(ma)007:2787: rdo rje chos su dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2788: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na snang ba mtha' yas
NK016(ma)007:2789: kyi rang bzhin so sor rtog pa'i ye shes snang
NK016(ma)007:2791: 'du shes kyi phung po snang ba mtha' yas su
NK016(ma)007:2792: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes rna ltag g.yon du
NK016(ma)007:2793: bum chu thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yi //
NK016(ma)007:2794: 'gro don mnyam pa med pa yis //
NK016(ma)007:2795: phrag dog rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)007:2796: gnyis su med par dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2797: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa don yod grub pa'i rang bzhin
NK016(ma)007:2798: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes don grub phrag dog
NK016(ma)007:2799: dag / 'du byed kyi phung po don yod grub
NK016(ma)007:2800: par bya ba grub pa'i ye shes bum chu dpral
NK016(ma)007:2801: bar rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)007:2802: gti mug rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)007:2803: cis kyang mi chod mi shigs pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:2804: rdo rje'i ming du rab tu grags /
NK016(ma)007:2805: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha rnam par snang mdzad kyi rang
NK016(ma)007:2806: bzhin me long lta bu'i ye shes rnam snang gti
NK016(ma)007:2807: mug dag gzugs kyi phung po rnam par snang mdzad
NK016(ma)007:2808: du me long lta bu'i ye shes zhes rtogs pa
NK016(ma)007:2809: bskyed / skabs su bab na dbu rgyan bcing ba dang /
NK016(ma)007:2810: rdor dril gtod pa rnams byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:2811: de dang de'i mthar chus kyang dbang bskur ba sngar ltar bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:2812: de'i mthar sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2813: sku'am phyag mtshan nam phyag rgya gnas gsum du bzhag la /
NK016(ma)007:2814: spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po sogs nas /
NK016(ma)007:2815: tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:2816: zhes pa'i bar gzhan sngar dang 'dra ba las sngags tshan so so'i gong du /
NK016(ma)007:2817: dpal ldan sangs rgyas sku 'chang ba //
NK016(ma)007:2818: rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi sku //
NK016(ma)007:2819: deng bdag sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK016(ma)007:2820: sku yi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2822: gsung dang thugs kyang de bzhin du bsgyur bas so //
NK016(ma)007:2823: de ltar slob ma mchod pa'i yul du gyur pa la kun bzang /
NK016(ma)007:2825: bzhi bsnol gyis mchod par bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:2826: gnyis pa mkha' 'gro ma gtor ma'i dbang gis gsang ba'i ye shes byin dbab pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2828: rkang rting sprad nas rtse mo btsugs /
NK016(ma)007:2830: lag gnyis grub mo phyir brgyangs pas spyi bor gtor ma bzung /
NK016(ma)007:2831: rtsa dang nywa bzhi grib gyis sgrim pa ni lus kyi las so //
NK016(ma)007:2833: sarba r+au pa ba lim ta p+au dza kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:2835: gang shar rtsol med du klod la smrar gzhug /
NK016(ma)007:2836: sems kyi las snod kyi 'jig rten b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i
NK016(ma)007:2837: gtor gzhong du rgya tshad med pa'i zla ba la
NK016(ma)007:2838: gnas pa'i bcud kyi sems can thams cad kyi lus
NK016(ma)007:2839: dang longs spyod dge ba'i rtsa ba dang bcas pa
NK016(ma)007:2840: thams cad / phung khams kyi chos can rang bzhin
NK016(ma)007:2841: lhun grub dam tshig gi rdzas su dag pa la
NK016(ma)007:2842: spyi bo'i gtor ma ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin bdud
NK016(ma)007:2843: rtsi'i dwangs ma sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye shes
NK016(ma)007:2844: dang ro mnyam pa chu bo'i rgyun bzhin du babs
NK016(ma)007:2845: nas ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i bdud rtsi'i mchod sprin
NK016(ma)007:2847: 'khor 'das thams cad mchod yul du dag pa'i sku
NK016(ma)007:2848: gsung thugs kyi gsang ba rang bzhin dbyings kyi mkha'
NK016(ma)007:2849: 'gro mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo dang slob
NK016(ma)007:2850: ma'i lus ngag yid gsum ro gcig pa bde ba
NK016(ma)007:2851: chen por 'bar pa la sems 'dzin du bcug la
NK016(ma)007:2852: / cang te'u sogs rol mo'i sgra sbyar zhing /
NK016(ma)007:2853: sha chen gyi spos sreg pa dang bcas pas 'khor
NK016(ma)007:2854: 'das thams cad dag pa rab 'byams rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK016(ma)007:2855: 'khor chen por yongs su sad par byas la /
NK016(ma)007:2856: bla ma brgyud pa'i mtshan shar dang yi dam zhi khro'i sngags rnams brjod pa'i mthar /
NK016(ma)007:2858: rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma dam pa rnams dang yi
NK016(ma)007:2859: dam zhi khro rab 'byams sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK016(ma)007:2862: rigs drug gi sems can lha'i 'khor lor dag pa dang bcas pa thams cad la /
NK016(ma)007:2863: slob bu'i lus longs spyod dge tshogs rgya mtsho dang
NK016(ma)007:2864: bcas pa thams cad srid zhi dbyer med kyi bdud
NK016(ma)007:2865: rtsi chen por sbyar zhing spel ba 'di 'bul zhing
NK016(ma)007:2866: mchis na gnyis su med par bzhes te gnas skabs
NK016(ma)007:2867: dang mthar thug gi phyi nang gsang ba'i bar chad
NK016(ma)007:2868: mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)007:2869: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK016(ma)007:2874: rigs drug gi sems can lha'i 'khor lor dag pa
NK016(ma)007:2875: rnams la zhes tha dad du phye na'ang legs par
NK016(ma)007:2876: 'gyur ro // de'i tshe lus 'phar zhing g.yo ba dang /
NK016(ma)007:2877: ngag smra zhing rgod pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2878: sems rtog med 'od gsal gyi dbyings su grol ba'i nyams rnams byung rgyal du bskyang du gzhug /
NK016(ma)007:2879: gtor ma gnas su bzhag nas bla ma la spyi bos gtugs pa'i yon dbul lo //
NK016(ma)007:2880: gsum pa kun tu bzang po'i rig pa rtsal gyi
NK016(ma)007:2881: dbang gis lhag pa'i ye shes ngo sprad pa la
NK016(ma)007:2882: gsum las / dang po rtags kun tu bzang po mtshon par byed pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2883: slob bus man+dala phul nas thal mo sbyar la /
NK016(ma)007:2885: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK016(ma)007:2886: rdo rje bla ma dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2887: yang dag don gyi mchog dam pa //
NK016(ma)007:2888: bdag la mngon du gyur par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:2890: de nas slob bus stan bde ba la rnam snang gi chos bdun bcas la /
NK016(ma)007:2891: sems kyi rten snying gar kun tu bzang po mthing
NK016(ma)007:2892: ga mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can rdo rje'i skyil
NK016(ma)007:2893: mo krung gis bzhugs par bskyed la /
NK016(ma)007:2894: e h+ye his ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)007:2895: dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis med du bstim la /
NK016(ma)007:2896: rdo rje rtse lnga pa gtad de /
NK016(ma)007:2897: 'di ni rang rig 'gyur ba med pa'i don ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i rtags yin no //
NK016(ma)007:2899: gnyis pa don kun tu bzang po ngo sprad pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2901: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'di //
NK016(ma)007:2902: kun tu bzang pos ston par dka' //
NK016(ma)007:2904: rdo rje sems dpas mtshon du med //
NK016(ma)007:2905: rig pa sems kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK016(ma)007:2906: spros med rnam dag ye shes yin //
NK016(ma)007:2907: kun gzhi ye nas ma bcos pa //
NK016(ma)007:2908: bde chen rang shar klong du zhog /
NK016(ma)007:2909: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)007:2910: zhes pas sems skad cig ma gang skyes de ka rtsol bral bsal bzhag med par bzhag la /
NK016(ma)007:2911: sems kyi gshis gang du'ang ma grub pa /
NK016(ma)007:2912: mdangs bde chen du ma 'gag pa /
NK016(ma)007:2913: rtsal sna tshogs su snang ba /
NK016(ma)007:2914: bsgom bya sgom byed thams cad las 'das pa'i gsal
NK016(ma)007:2915: rig rjen ne ba spros pa dang bral ba de
NK016(ma)007:2916: ka ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin don kun tu bzang
NK016(ma)007:2917: po yin no // zhes ngo sprad /
NK016(ma)007:2918: gsum pa nyams kun tu bzang po bskyang du gzhugs pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2919: a snang stong dbyer med chos sku la //
NK016(ma)007:2920: rig stong bde ba chen por shar //
NK016(ma)007:2921: zung 'jug spros dang bral ba de //
NK016(ma)007:2922: kun tu bzang po'i ngo bo'o //
NK016(ma)007:2923: bod+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu
NK016(ma)007:2924: +aah zhes pas rjes shes gang shar gyi skye 'gag
NK016(ma)007:2925: gnas gsum gyi rang ngo la bltas pas rang grol
NK016(ma)007:2926: gyi ye shes gsal la mi rtog pa ni nyams
NK016(ma)007:2927: kun tu bzang po yin te /
NK016(ma)007:2929: sngar rjes mi dpyad 'das pa'i 'du shes dor //
NK016(ma)007:2930: phyis sngun mi bsu yid kyi 'brel thag bcad //
NK016(ma)007:2931: bar du 'dzin med nam mkha'i ngang la bzhag /
NK016(ma)007:2932: ces pa ltar bskyang du gzhug go //
NK016(ma)007:2933: bzhi pa dam pa rigs brgya phyag rgya'i dbang gis
NK016(ma)007:2934: dag pa'i snang ba rab 'byams su bstan pa ni
NK016(ma)007:2935: / slob bu seng ges btegs pa'i khri la bcom
NK016(ma)007:2936: ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yum dang bcas
NK016(ma)007:2937: pa'i rnam pas 'khod pa la dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK016(ma)007:2938: tshogs rnams mar me gcig las gnyis chad kyi tshul
NK016(ma)007:2939: du rim bzhin byon nas gnyis med du thim par
NK016(ma)007:2940: / bsam la / rgyas par na phyag gi bkol
NK016(ma)007:2941: byang las 'byung ba bzhin la 'don pa bsgyur ba'i
NK016(ma)007:2942: mthar so so'i sngags dang bcas pas re re bzhin
NK016(ma)007:2943: / bsam la / du bskur zhing / 'bring du
NK016(ma)007:2944: tshigs bcad kyis bsdus pa bzhin sde tshan du byas
NK016(ma)007:2945: / bsam la / du bskur zhing / nas dang / shin tu bsdus pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2946: bum pa gtso bo'i phyag rgya dang bcas pas spyi bor bzhag la /
NK016(ma)007:2947: mi rtog rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK016(ma)007:2948: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK016(ma)007:2949: thugs rje'i bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK016(ma)007:2950: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs brgyas dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)007:2953: badz+r+ai b+ha wa a b+hi shiny+tsa m+ai /
NK016(ma)007:2955: 'di ltar chos thams cad dam pa rigs brgya'i ngo bor dag cing /
NK016(ma)007:2956: de yang rang sems lhag pa bden gnyis dbyer med
NK016(ma)007:2957: gsang chen rigs gcig tu rnam par dag pa yin
NK016(ma)007:2958: no // zhes rtogs pa bskyed do //
NK016(ma)007:2960: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas sngags kyi phreng ba thon /
NK016(ma)007:2961: slob ma'i khar zhugs te snying gar thim par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:2962: zhi khro'i spyi sngags dang yig brgya'i rjes zlos lan gsum du byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:2963: sgom bzlas kyi dam bca' blang /
NK016(ma)007:2964: slob mas man+dala phul te phyag btsal nas thal mo sbyar la /
NK016(ma)007:2965: gtso bos ji ltar bka' stsal pa //
NK016(ma)007:2966: de dag thams cad bdag gis bgyid //
NK016(ma)007:2967: ces dam bcas te yon gyi dngos po ci 'byor ba dbul lo //
NK016(ma)007:2968: tshogs mchod kyi nang tshan bzhi ba tshogs la rol pa ni /
NK016(ma)007:2969: las kyi rdo rjes phyag sngon du 'gro bas thabs shes kyi rdzas rnams bsnol mar stob cing /
NK016(ma)007:2970: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas dpal //
NK016(ma)007:2971: log rtog mtshan ma'i spros pa ngang gis zhi //
NK016(ma)007:2972: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder spyad nas kyang //
NK016(ma)007:2973: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:2975: des kyang pad+ma'i phyag rgyas bskor zhing /
NK016(ma)007:2978: 'dus pa thams cad la brims te /
NK016(ma)007:2979: nang gi sbyin sreg gis rol ba'i mthar /
NK016(ma)007:2980: hoh bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam
NK016(ma)007:2981: dral rnams kyis dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro
NK016(ma)007:2982: ba ma lus pa dbang du 'du bar gyur cig
NK016(ma)007:2983: / ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen por gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:2984: rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dang lang tsho la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:2985: zhal zas kyi bye brag mang po gsol bas zhi
NK016(ma)007:2986: khro'i phrin las kyi rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs la dbang
NK016(ma)007:2989: lnga pa lhag ma btang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:2990: lhag ma rnams gsog 'jog med par bsdus pa dang /
NK016(ma)007:2991: sngar gyi phud lhag bcas dkyil 'khor gyi shar lhor dri'i man+dala gyi khar bzhag /
NK016(ma)007:2992: slob dpon gyi lce la rta mgrin yab yum rol
NK016(ma)007:2993: pa mdzad pa'i byang sems bdud rtsir bab par bsam
NK016(ma)007:2994: la / mkha' dbyings kyi rgyas dza gad kyi kha phru btab la /
NK016(ma)007:2995: gu ru kro d+ha rat+na sa ma ya p+r+ai sha
NK016(ma)007:2996: purba bud+d+ha k+she tra p+aa la k+sho b+ha ka ra
NK016(ma)007:2997: h+aum phata / ces pas byin gyis brlab /
NK016(ma)007:2999: las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK016(ma)007:3000: mkha' 'gro lhag sdud ma sring ging gi tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:3001: lhag ma kha chu'i dam la gtogs pa rnams //
NK016(ma)007:3002: dam tshig bzhin du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:3003: e +aa ral+li hrim hrim dzahh+aum bam hoh d+aa ki ni h+aum dzah zhes pas spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)007:3006: ma bdun sring bzhi 'bar ma brgyad //
NK016(ma)007:3007: pho nya la sogs lhag sdud tshogs //
NK016(ma)007:3008: dpal gyi pham phabs 'di gsol la //
NK016(ma)007:3009: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:3010: mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis //
NK016(ma)007:3012: dbang phyug ma nyi shu brgyad /
NK016(ma)007:3013: dpal ldan nag po re ma t+ai /
NK016(ma)007:3017: pho nya sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa rnams
NK016(ma)007:3018: kyi zhal du ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa
NK016(ma)007:3019: hi / ma h+aa rak+ta kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:3020: ma h+aa ba lid+ha kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)007:3022: hoh lhag sdud kyi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha'
NK016(ma)007:3023: 'gro dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK016(ma)007:3024: rnams lhag ma'i dam tshig 'dis tshim zhing dgyes par
NK016(ma)007:3025: gyur te / dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skongs nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK016(ma)007:3027: dge 'dun dang chos kyi rgyal srid skyongs /
NK016(ma)007:3029: sems can gyi phan bde spel /
NK016(ma)007:3030: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi stong grogs mdzod /
NK016(ma)007:3031: sngags 'chang rnams kyi phrin las sgrubs /
NK016(ma)007:3032: khyad par dam tshig 'dir 'dus pa rnams kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i 'gal rkyen zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)007:3033: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa myur du 'grub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK016(ma)007:3036: zhes pas mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par bsam la lhag ma dor zhing dkyil 'khor bsdu'o //
NK016(ma)007:3037: gsum pa brtan ma bskyang ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:3038: phyi rol tu brtan mi'i gtor ma sman phud kyis bran la /
NK016(ma)007:3039: tram rat+na tree lo kya phata /
NK016(ma)007:3041: gtor ma'i rdul phra rab re re zhing rin po
NK016(ma)007:3042: che'i gur khang longs spyod zad mi shes pas nam
NK016(ma)007:3046: tshogs dang bka' yi tshogs bcas nyid //
NK016(ma)007:3047: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK016(ma)007:3048: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK016(ma)007:3049: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:3050: bdag nyid chen mo la sogs bdud mo bzhi //
NK016(ma)007:3051: gangs dkar sha med la sogs gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK016(ma)007:3052: kong btsun de mo la sogs sman mo bzhi //
NK016(ma)007:3053: bod khams skyong ba'i che zhe chen mo rnams //
NK016(ma)007:3054: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK016(ma)007:3055: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK016(ma)007:3056: sil snyan mang po'i sgra dang bcas //
NK016(ma)007:3057: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:3058: che zhe chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK016(ma)007:3059: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK016(ma)007:3061: rlangs chen dpal gyi seng ge yis //
NK016(ma)007:3062: zhing chen stan la bkod nas kyang //
NK016(ma)007:3063: lag tu rdo rje gtad nas ni //
NK016(ma)007:3064: dbang bskur gsang ba'i mtshan nas brjod //
NK016(ma)007:3065: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK016(ma)007:3066: bod khams bsrung zhing skyong ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:3067: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs bya zhes //
NK016(ma)007:3068: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK016(ma)007:3069: g.yar dam gnyan po rjes dgongs la //
NK016(ma)007:3070: dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma longs //
NK016(ma)007:3071: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK016(ma)007:3077: ma ma srim 'gro ma h+aum b+h+yo h+aum h+aum /
NK016(ma)007:3079: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs sman rag gtor gsum gyis mchod cing /
NK016(ma)007:3081: brtan ma bcu gnyis 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis
NK016(ma)007:3082: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs sogs kyis phrin las
NK016(ma)007:3083: bcol nas / ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol nas gtor ma gtsang sar bskyal lo //
NK016(ma)007:3084: bzhi pa dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:3085: btang rag gi mchod pa bshams shing byin gyis brlabs te /
NK016(ma)007:3089: sman gtor rak+tara bcas pas mchod cing bstod nas /
NK016(ma)007:3091: yi dam zhi khro rigs gcig dkyil 'khor du //
NK016(ma)007:3092: sgrub rdzas dman zhing ting 'dzin cho ga nyams //
NK016(ma)007:3093: 'gal 'khrul nongs pa ci mchis bzod par gsol //
NK016(ma)007:3094: tshangs pa mchog gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)007:3096: yi ge brgya pa bzlas pas bzod gsol byas la /
NK016(ma)007:3098: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK016(ma)007:3099: ji srid nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can
NK016(ma)007:3100: thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK016(ma)007:3101: sa la ma bzhag gi bar du rgyal ba rnams
NK016(ma)007:3102: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar brtan par bzhugs su
NK016(ma)007:3103: gsol / khyad par du'ang ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)007:3104: 'di nyid la ji srid 'byung ba bzhi'i gnod pas
NK016(ma)007:3105: ma zhig gi bar du brtan par bzhugs su gsol
NK016(ma)007:3106: gsol / // brtan par bzhugs nas bdag dang sems
NK016(ma)007:3107: can thams cad la mchog dang thun mong gi dngos
NK016(ma)007:3108: grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK016(ma)007:3109: su pra tish+tha badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)007:3110: zhes pas brtan bzhugs byas la /
NK016(ma)007:3111: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+he h+aum /
NK016(ma)007:3112: s+w+aa +aam h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)007:3113: zhes pas dam tshig gi 'khor lo gsal btab la /
NK016(ma)007:3114: badz+ra pad+ma sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)007:3117: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK016(ma)007:3118: dzahh+aum bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK016(ma)007:3119: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyi sprin 'phros pas snod bcud thams cad dag cing gsal bar byas /
NK016(ma)007:3121: dag pa'i snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang la thim /
NK016(ma)007:3123: 'khor rnams rim bzhin gtso bo yab yum la /
NK016(ma)007:3124: yum yab la de ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK016(ma)007:3127: h+aum gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du thim nas rnam
NK016(ma)007:3128: par rtog med lhun grub nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang
NK016(ma)007:3131: ces pas thun mtshams kyi lhar langs te /
NK016(ma)007:3132: snang grags rig gsum lha sngags chos nyid kyi rang bzhin du shes par byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:3135: mgrin par +aah snying gar h+aum yig rnams kyis mtshan par bsam la /
NK016(ma)007:3136: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK016(ma)007:3138: lus rdo rje'i go chas zhu lugs su g.yogs pas
NK016(ma)007:3139: sgo gsum rdo rje gsum dang dbyer mi phyed par
