NK016(ma)007:3140: bsam zhing / thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)007:3141: sku gsung thugs kyis kun la khyab //
NK016(ma)007:3142: ces brjod cing nga rgyal bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:3143: rdul tshon gyi cho ga zhag sbrel du byed ba'i nyin snga ma rnams la'ang de kho na dang /
NK016(ma)007:3147: ye shes kyi 'khor lo nam mkhar btegs nas /
NK016(ma)007:3148: gtang rag gi mchod bstod dang bzod gsol byas nas //
NK016(ma)007:3149: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK016(ma)007:3151: dz+ny+aa na man+dala badz+ra muh zhes pas gshegs su gsol la /
NK016(ma)007:3152: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bsdu tshul sngar bzhin byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:3153: dus de nyid dam nang par lha'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas /
NK016(ma)007:3155: rdo rje dang bcas pa'i lag gis thog mar lha mtshan rnams bsdus la cung zad mgo bor bkod /
NK016(ma)007:3156: de nas dbang ldan nas brtsams te gtso bo'i gnas
NK016(ma)007:3157: kyi bar rim gyis phyags la cung zad tsam gzhan
NK016(ma)007:3158: la'ang byin / lhag ma rnams snod bzang por blugs
NK016(ma)007:3159: nas mchod pa dang bkur sti chen pos chu klung
NK016(ma)007:3160: la'ang byin / du bor ro // bum chu lhag
NK016(ma)007:3161: ma la sogs bas kyang gzhan la phan par bya'o
NK016(ma)007:3162: la'ang byin / du bor ro // // lnga pa bsngo ba shis brjod bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)007:3163: bla ma yi dam lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)007:3164: deng 'dir brtson pas bsgrubs pa'i dge ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:3165: dus gsum bsags dang yod pa'i dge ba rnams //
NK016(ma)007:3166: bsdom te bla med byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK016(ma)007:3167: deng nas byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK016(ma)007:3168: rigs bzang blo gsal nga rgyal med pa dang //
NK016(ma)007:3169: snying rje che zhing bla ma la gus ldan //
NK016(ma)007:3170: dpal ldan rdo rje'i theg la nges gnas shog /
NK016(ma)007:3171: dbang gis smin cing dam tshig sdom par ldan //
NK016(ma)007:3172: rim gnyis lam la bsnyen sgrub mthar phyin te //
NK016(ma)007:3173: dka' ba med par rig 'dzin go 'phang bgrod //
NK016(ma)007:3174: dngos grub rnam gnyis bde blag 'grub gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:3175: cir snang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'khor lor rdzogs //
NK016(ma)007:3176: grags pa thams cad brjod bral sngags kyi sgra //
NK016(ma)007:3177: sems kyi 'gyu ba rang rig 'dus ma byas //
NK016(ma)007:3178: bde chen 'du 'bral med pa mngon gyur shog /
NK016(ma)007:3179: nyams chag rtogs sgrib ma spangs gnas su dag /
NK016(ma)007:3180: phyi nang gsang ba dbyer med rtogs pas bskangs //
NK016(ma)007:3181: gang shar rang grol kun bzang klong yangs su //
NK016(ma)007:3182: ngan song dong sprugs srid zhi mnyam gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:3183: thig le chen por sku dang zhing khams rdzogs //
NK016(ma)007:3184: dam tshig chen por spang blang mtshan ma dag /
NK016(ma)007:3185: khyab gdal chen por re dogs mdud pa grol //
NK016(ma)007:3186: rdzogs pa chen por chos sku mngon gyur shog /
NK016(ma)007:3187: brgyud pa gsum gyi byin rlabs snying la zhugs //
NK016(ma)007:3188: sgyu 'phrul d+r+aa ba'i lam gsang sems la rdzogs //
NK016(ma)007:3189: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub pa yis //
NK016(ma)007:3190: mu mtha' med pa'i 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK016(ma)007:3191: zhi khro sprul pa'i 'khor los lung ston zhing //
NK016(ma)007:3192: mkha' 'gro rnams kyis bu bzhin skyong ba dang //
NK016(ma)007:3193: chos skyong srung mas bar chad kun bsal nas //
NK016(ma)007:3194: yid la smon pa mtha' dag 'grub gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:3195: rgyal ba'i bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK016(ma)007:3196: bstan 'dzin rnams kyi bzhed pa'i don kun grub //
NK016(ma)007:3197: ma lus skye dgu'i 'gal rkyen kun zhi zhing //
NK016(ma)007:3198: phun tshogs mtha' dag yid bzhin 'byor gyur cig /
NK016(ma)007:3201: dga' ston bya ba sogs mtha' rgyas kyi cho ga rnams gsang ba spyi'i 'gros bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK016(ma)007:3202: rigs rgya'i khyab bdag dpal ldan rdo rje sems //
NK016(ma)007:3203: thugs rje'i rnam 'phrul mtha' yas 'gro rgyud kyi //
NK016(ma)007:3204: sdug bsngal rgyu bcas bsal nas sku bzhi yi //
NK016(ma)007:3205: bde chen mchog la 'god byed myur ba'i lam //
NK016(ma)007:3206: rtsa ba'i mdo dang rjes 'brel gzhung rnams kyi //
NK016(ma)007:3207: dgongs don rgya bod mkhas grub ji snyed pas //
NK016(ma)007:3208: gsal bar mdzad pa'i gsung gi snying po'i don //
NK016(ma)007:3209: brjod bde'i ngag gis khrigs su 'dir bsdebs so //
NK016(ma)007:3210: bsod nams bla med ston zla ltar dkar bas //
NK016(ma)007:3211: 'gro 'di'i sgrib gnyis mun pa yongs bsal nas //
NK016(ma)007:3212: bde chen snang ba 'byams klas rigs brgya yi //
NK016(ma)007:3213: ye shes 'khor lo gcig tu 'grub gyur cig //
NK016(ma)007:3214: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' gsang chen rigs bsdus kyi
NK016(ma)007:3215: cho ga bde chen lam bzang zhes bya ba 'di
NK016(ma)007:3216: ni / shing rta chen po sangs rgyas gsang ba
NK016(ma)007:3217: dang bi ma la mi tra'i man ngag gi bka'
NK016(ma)007:3218: srol bzhin sngar khrigs su bkod pa las don gcig
NK016(ma)007:3219: tshig gi brjod pa tha dad pa rnams 'don bde
NK016(ma)007:3220: ba'i slad du phyis khrom sprugs kyi chog khrigs bkod
NK016(ma)007:3221: pa dang mthun par byas nas /
NK016(ma)007:3222: slar yang rig pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med rdo rjes
NK016(ma)007:3223: ji ltar bkod pa bzhin du gnas brtan lo ts+aa
NK016(ma)007:3224: ba ngag gi dbang phyug chos dpal rgya mtshos gtsang
NK016(ma)007:3226: o rgyan smin grol gling gi gtsug lag khang du
NK016(ma)007:3227: rnam gnon gyi lo cho 'phrul chen po'i dus chen
